                                                                                                                                             (1, 'client_refer', 'Your best source of new business is referrals from happy customers or clients. You cannot receive a better lead than one that has been sent your way with a strong referral. You cannot have a more motivated prospect arrive in your business than someone sent there by a raving fan.', '<strong>refering a client</strong> - new clients only.', 'Referring another client', 0, 'LOYALTY'),
                                                                                                                                             (4, 'client_rebook', 'Pre-booking is merely the practice of asking your client\'s for the permission to book their next appointments before they check out. Pre-booking increases productivity, drives revenue, helps with staff retention and improves customer loyalty.', '<strong> prebooking each service</strong> - at ringup only.', 'Reward for prebooking each service at time of ring up', 0, 'LOYALTY'),
                                                                                                                                             (7, 'client_new_service', '', '<strong> trying an entire new service</strong> - at ringup only.', 'Reward for trying a new service.', 1, 'LOYALTY'),
