                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           (87923, 0, 'Appointment confirmation', 'Your appointment details', '<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n</head>\n<body>\n<table border=\"0\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\">\n<div align=\"center\">\n<table width=\"600\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" bgcolor=\"#ffffff\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"padding-left: 10px; font-family: Helvetica,Arial,Verdana,sans-serif;\" align=\"left\"><br /><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://scontent.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/10402593_757903654264231_853722833027562135_n.jpg?oh=fb1689e7f14be1fec8d8c9622ecedd85&amp;oe=57F633F4\" alt=\"\" width=\"199\" height=\"199\" />\n<h2>Booking Confirmation</h2>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">\n<div style=\"border: 1px  solid  #bdbdbd; border-radius: 8px;\">\n<div style=\"padding-left: 10px; font-family: Helvetica,Arial,Verdana,sans-serif;\">\n<h4>Hi [APPOINTMENTNAME],</h4>\n<div style=\"padding-left: 10px;\"><strong>Thank you so much for choosing morgans spa. Your appointment has now been confirmed.</strong>\n<p><br /><strong>Booking Details:</strong></p>\n<table style=\"font-family: helvetica,Arial,Tahoma,sans-serif;\" width=\"426\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"text-align: left; background-color: #f0f0f0;\"><th style=\"padding-left: 5px;\" colspan=\"2\">Item</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"background-color: #f6f6f6; font-size: 14px; color: #333333; width: 400px;\" colspan=\"2\">\n<table style=\"padding: 2px; margin: 0px  0px  0px  5px; width: 100%; font-size: 12px; font-family: helvetica,Arial,Tahoma,sans-serif;\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"padding-left: 20px; width: 100%;\">\n<td style=\"width: 110px; padding: 2px  0; font-weight: bold;\">Details</td>\n<td>\n<p>[COMPANYNAME]<br />([ATYPE])</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"padding-left: 20px; width: 100%;\">\n<td style=\"width: 110px; padding: 2px  0; font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;</td>\n<td>[ADATE] [ASTARTTIME]</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"padding-left: 20px; width: 100%;\">\n<td style=\"width: 110px; padding: 2px  0; font-weight: bold;\">With</td>\n<td>[AWITH]</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"padding-left: 20px; width: 100%;\">\n<td style=\"width: 110px; padding: 2px  0; font-weight: bold;\">Address</td>\n<td>[COMPANYNAME]<br />[COMPANYSTREET]<br /> [COMPANYCITY]<br />[COMPANYCOUNTRY]<br /><a href=\"https://maps.google.com/maps?q=[COMPANYNAME]\" target=\"_blank\">(View on map)</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"padding-left: 20px; width: 100%;\">\n<td style=\"width: 110px; padding: 2px  0; font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;</td>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<br clear=\"all\" />\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>SPA TERMS, CONDITIONS &amp; ETIQUETTE<br /><br />We recommend pre booking your treatments &amp; packages to avoid dissapointment!<br />Also please note you are accepting our terms &amp; conditions when making your reservation.<br /><br />ARRIVAL TIMES<br /><br /></strong>All times given on your reservation are arrival times &amp; are not your allocated treatment time. Some spa reservations do however start with your treatment time. Your treatment time will be given to you on your arrival.<br /><br /><strong>LATENESS<br /><br /></strong>Please arrive 15 minutes before your arrival time. This will give you adequate time to fill in you consultation card, use the rest room if needed, and enjoy a light refreshment in our reception area. Arriving late may result in reducing your treatment time, as our team our on a strict schedule. We will always try our best to accommodate and do allow 10 minutes, with us performing the best treatment we can in the time that is remaining.Anything over this could cause your treatment to be cancelled without reschedule and at full charge. We do understand that arriving late is sometimes out of your control, but our schedules are detrimental to the smooth running of the business for&nbsp;<em>every</em> client. To avoid these situations we do recommend that you plan ahead, taking into consideration our city location, parking, and travel time. We are more than happy to advise you on any of these issues prior to your visit.<br /><br /><strong>PAYMENTS, DEPOSITS &amp; CANCELLATIONS<br /><br /></strong>We require a minimum 50% deposit on&nbsp;<em>all</em> bookings. This payment is made on booking to secure your chosen date and arrival time. All booking are&nbsp;<em>non-refundable,&nbsp;</em>however, with a minimum of 72 hours we are more than willing to transfer your appointment date to one that is available to you. Any cancellations or no shows under the 72 hour threshold will result in the loss of your 50% deposit.&nbsp;<br /><br /><strong>REFUND POLICY<br /><br /></strong>Due to personal&nbsp;hygiene and health &amp; safety reasons, we cannot give refunds on&nbsp;<em>any products</em> purchased. All of our retail stock is brand new and for personal use only, as recommended&nbsp;<em>for you</em> by our fully qualified staff. All our treatments our performed by qualified therapists. If you have concerns regarding your treatment please contact us immediately. We will look into any concerns immediately but please note we&nbsp;<em>cannot give refunds.</em><br /><br /><strong>AGE RESTRICTIONS<br /><br /></strong>For health &amp; safety reasons and to allow us to maintain a peaceful and relaxing environment, anyone under the age of 18 are not permitted within the spa.&nbsp;<br /><br /><strong>HEALTH CONDITIONS<br /><br /></strong>All of our spa guests are required to complete a client consultation form. Failure to do so could result in us refusing your treatment choice, still at full cost of your spa package. Please advise us on any health conditions, allergies, current medications, injuries or recent surgeries within the last 18 months prior to your treatment. We do reserve the right to refuse treatment or offer an alternative, for health reasons if your treatment choice is unsuitable for you. In some cases we may require a GP or consultant note before using any facilities, or treatments to be carried out.<br /><br /><strong>NOISE LEVELS &amp; MOBILE PHONES<br /><br /></strong>Could we pease ask you to respect all other guests by maintaining a considerate volume in all areas of the spa. Mobile phones must be kept on silent or turned off, and are not permitted in the treatment rooms. Please be aware you may be asked to decrease your volume.&nbsp;<br /><br /><strong>CLEANLINESS<br /><br /></strong>Cleanliness is something our spa prides itself on, in keeping with that commitment, and with health &amp; safety guidelines, our equipment is fully sterilised after every treatment or service given.<br /><br /><strong>LOSS OR DAMAGES<br /><br /></strong>We recommend that you do not bring with you any valuable or sentimental belongings. We cannot be held responsible for any loss or damage to&nbsp;<em>any&nbsp;</em>of your belongings you&nbsp;<em>choose&nbsp;</em>to bring.<br /><br /><strong>We hope you enjoy your experience with us today &amp; in the future!</strong></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">\n<p style=\"padding-left: 10px; font-family: Helvetica,Arial,Verdana,sans-serif; color: #999; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 5px;\"><a href=\"https://maps.google.com/maps?q=+[COMPANYSTREET]+,+[COMPANYCITY],+[COMPANYCOUNTRY]\" target=\"_blank\">&nbsp;</a></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p><img style=\"height: 1px; width: 1px; border-width: 0; padding: 0; margin: 0;\" src=\"https://prelive-crm.pabau.com/program/blocked.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\"