                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           (103542, 0, '3D Lipo Cavitation and Cellulite After care', '3D Lipo Aftercare Information', 'Hi [APPOINTMENTFIRSTNAME]<br /><br />Great to see you in the clinic, I hope you enjoyed your treatment with us. We\'ll be excited to see your results develop over the coming weeks!<br /><br />Just a reminder not to forget to follow the aftercare advice that we discussed; this will help your body achieve the best results possible following your treatment.<br /><br />1. Drink at least 2.5 litres of water per day &ndash; This has a HUGE impact on your results and will support your lymphatic system to eliminate the fat cells over the next 8 weeks. <br /><br />This is Very Important to achieve the best results!<br /><br />2. Maintain your weight - Obviously you won&rsquo;t be planning to put weight on but it is really important that you (at least) maintain your weight.<br /><br />3. Eat a healthy diet and maybe do a bit of exercise &ndash; This helps with #2! I often find that having these treatments really motivates clients to be a bit healthier and can kick start a lifestyle change. Exercise also helps to boost your lymphatic circulation so it could support your results.<br /><br />4. Limit caffeine and alcohol intake &ndash; Again, this is all to do with supporting your liver in its job of eliminating the dead fat cells. If your liver is busy metabolising toxins such as caffeine and alcohol it could potentially slow down the elimination process. <br /><br />5. Avoid - Caffeinated drinks 2 hours before or after your treatment and try not to have alcohol 24 hours before or after.<br /><br />6. Limit - Calories and carbs on the days of your treatments if possible. We release energy during cavitation which we want to burn off as quickly as possible.<br /><br /><strong>Did we mention The Body Clinic Refer a Friend Rewards?</strong><br /><br />We really appreciate receiving referrals from our clients. So if you feel like talking about us and spreading the word about our little clinic and our treatments, as a really BIG THANK YOU we want to reward you.<br /><br />If anyone, who you refer to us, has any treatment we&rsquo;ll reward you with a voucher for &pound;50! You can spend this on any treatment in the clinic.<br /><br />If you have any questions at all please feel free to give us a call. <br /><br />Kind regards<br /><br /><strong>Kate</strong><br /><br />The Body Clinic<br />Tel: 01562 887743<br />Em: <a href=\"mailto:info@thebodyclinic.uk.com\">info@thebodyclinic.uk.com<br /><img src=\"cdn/template_archive/267b22ba97b4654b38f7b2a4921c217e.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"277\" height=\"87\" /></a><br /><br />', 0, 'email', '2016-09-15 13:08:22', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, '', '', 0, 'aftercare', '', '', 0, 0),
