 your immune system, aids with jet lag, enhances your hair growth and detoxes your body. These are just a few ways of how these vitadrips can benefit you, but we advise having a consultation with one of our practitioners so they can discuss with you what you\'re looking to achieve and advise on the best vitadrip for you.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">I have attached The Elixir Clinic brochure as well as a price list of the services we offer in our London clinic.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">To book or rearrange an appointment please contact us on <a href=\"tel:020%207468%209748\" target=\"_blank\">0207 468 9748</a> or via email: <a href=\"mailto:info@theelixirclinic.com\" target=\"_blank\">info@theelixirclinic.com</a>.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><br />We look forward to hearing from you soon.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Kind Regards<br /><br /><br /></p>\n<p><strong>The Elixir Clinic</strong></p>\n<div>\n<div><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">LONDON | DUBAI | ABU DHABI</span></strong></div>\n<div><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">UK <a href=\"tel:020%207486%209748\" target=\"_blank\">+44 20 74869748</a>&nbsp;</span></div>\n<div>UAE +97 15 6299 2775 / 800ELIXIR (800-354947)</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</span></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">Follow us on Facebook:&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/theelixirclinic\" target=\"_blank\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?hl=en&amp;q=http://www.facebook.com/theelixirclinic&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1498298500949000&amp;usg=AFQjCNGe_5J7MikDwxagtwb5ETMb-k8aUg\">/theelixirclinic</a><br /></span></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: s