                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           (142828, 0, 'Initial Enquiry, Lower Eyelid Surgery AN', 'Your Complimentary Consultation Invitation', '<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n</head>\n<body>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Dear&nbsp;[LEADFNAME]<br /><br /></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It is lovely to hear from you regarding eyelid surgery. My name is Beau and it is my pleasure to introduce our excellent services to help you on your journey.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Lower Eyelid surgery is one of our most popular treatments and performed by our lead surgeon, Amir&nbsp;Nakhdjevani.<br /><br /></span></p>\n<p><em><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A Little About Us</span></em></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Our luxurious purpose built cosmetic clinic, in the idyllic&nbsp;Pantiles, Royal&nbsp;Tunbridge&nbsp;Wells, features three state of the art surgical theatres, quipped with the latest operating facilities, performing to the most exacting standards.<br /><br /><br />Situated within 1 hour of London and&nbsp;Gatwick&nbsp;Airport, we are in a perfect&nbsp;location, yet away from the hustle and bustle of the city.<br /></span></p>\n<strong><strong><br /></strong></strong>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.bellavou.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/BellaVou_HowToFindUs.pdf\">Click here to see where we are</a></p>\n<strong><strong><br /></strong></strong>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">All patient care is led by our highly skilled, British trained surgeons and their dedicated team of nurses and patient liaisons, to advise and care for you wherever you are in your journey. We are here for you.</span></p>\n<strong><strong><br /></strong></strong>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You must have so many questions about the treatment/s:</span></p>\n<strong><strong><br /></strong></strong>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">What are my options?</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">What does the treatment involve?</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Will it hurt?</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">How long will it take to recover?</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">How much does it cost?<br /><br /><a href=\"https://www.bellavou.co.uk/face/eyelid-surgery/\">(Click here to find some of the answers about eyelid surgery)</a><br /></span></p>\n<strong><strong><br /></strong></strong>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A complimentary consultation with one of our Specialist Surgeons, will help you to answer these questions and more.</span></p>\n<strong><strong><br /></strong></strong>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You will receive the best advice and recommendations and meet with our patient liaison team afterward. Your liaison will be your point of contact if there is anything you need, she will be there to help, in person, by phone or email.</span></p>\n<strong><strong><br /></strong></strong>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.bellavou.co.uk/book/\">Click here to arrange your Complimentary Consultation</a></p>\n<strong><strong><br /></strong></strong>\n<p><em><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Did you know?</span></em></p>\n<strong><strong><br /></strong></strong>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If distance or time pressures are a challenge, we offer&nbsp;Skype&nbsp;and&nbsp;Facetime&nbsp;consultations, for your convenience. Just remember to add this in the notes section when making your booking.</span></p>\n<strong><strong><br /></strong></strong>\n<p><em><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A Little More, Just For You.</span></em></p>\n<strong><strong><br /></strong></strong>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.realself.com/find/United-Kingdom/London/Plastic-Surgeon/Amir-Nakhdjevani\">Click here to Read What Our Patients Say About Us, and to See Their Before &amp; After Photos</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCUcF5IKH5r-0urle3FIWncQ/videos?view_as=subscriber\">We have a&nbsp;YouTube&nbsp;Channel, click here</a></p>\n<strong><strong><br /></strong></strong>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We look forward to meeting you and sharing your journey. Please do contact me if you would prefer to book your consultation directly and I will gladly let you know the next available appointment dates.</span></p>\n<strong><strong><br /></strong></strong>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Best Wishes</span></p>\n<strong><br /><strong>Beau&nbsp;Rich&nbsp;</strong><br /></strong>Front Of House Co-ordinator<strong><br /><br /><img src=\"https://ci4.googleusercontent.com/proxy/Ok11PdGzxwcARZ11psOZmBByktut_KMTNWJ--0WFaLsmyREVizCp_dlaC8b5ZNEijBZPPq1K8IGCdqRckCYvExwBInRZ4V5aco667_8NcmHcsOHEtU8LH9XSkh2k1Dk2JYGWcU8OTiTYNxI3-uM5_oBLBFSO43qrpeoTKzdsEJTy1muFn5R9-a4MAwT-N8afQPhQcd6S8QUM94obzHErQbuCAsYu=s0-d-e1-ft#https://storage.googleapis.com/signaturesatori/customer-C03twunv8/images/-2ec77daad95593cf8a9b7fc35526f2ae60485c75fb7628c03ad8baab9ab4ae3f.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"150\" /><br /><br /><a href=\"https://www.bellavou.co.uk/blog/realself-names-bella-vou-surgeon-europes-top-cosmetic-surgery-influencer/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Find out more about the&nbsp;RealSelf&nbsp;100</a><br /></strong><br />Bella&nbsp;Vou<br />Market House<br />45-47 The&nbsp;Pantiles<br />Royal&nbsp;Tunbridge&nbsp;Wells<br />Kent<br />TN2 5TE<br /><br /><a href=\"https://www.bellavou.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/BellaVou_HowToFindUs.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get directions to our clinic</a><br /><br />T&nbsp;01892 257 357&nbsp;|&nbsp;E&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:beau@bellavou.co.uk\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">beau@bellavou.co.uk</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;W&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.bellavou.co.uk/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://www.bellavou.co.uk</a><br /><br />This email and any attachments to it may be confidential and are intended solely for the use of the individual to whom it is addressed. Any views or opinions expressed are solely those of the author and do not necessarily represent those of Bella&nbsp;Vou.<br />If you are not the intended recipient of this email, you must neither take any action based upon its&nbsp;contents,&nbsp;nor copy or show it to anyone. Please contact the sender if you believe you have received this email in error.<strong><br /></strong>\n</body>\n</html>', 0, 'email', '2017-11-10 09:07:48', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, '', '', 0, 'general', '', '', 0, 0),
