602adf9ad4b5dabdd05f8c9f33.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"388\" height=\"258\" /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">____________________________________________________________________________________<br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #0000ff;\"><strong>REFLEXOLOGY</strong></span><br /><br />We welcome <a href=\"http://www.therapy-first.co.uk/our-team/johanna\" target=\"_blank\">Johanna</a> to our team! Johanna is an experienced reflexologist and is now offering treatments at our Media City clinic. Reflexology is a safe, natural therapy that helps relax, balance and harmonize the body. It may provide relief of symptoms of numerous health conditions and also help in reducing stress levels.<br /></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">For reflexology bookings, please&nbsp;email us on <a href=\"mailto:info@therapy-first.co.uk\">info@therapy-first.co.uk</a>&nbsp;and we&nbsp;do our best to accommodate you at a convenient time. Johanna is available at weekends as well as Mondays and Tuesdays (by appointment only). <br />Please note: you can book all our other treatments <a href=\"https://connect.pabau.com/bookings.php?compid=4603\" target=\"_blank\">ONLINE</a>.<br />____________________________________________________________________________________<br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong><sup>HYPOPRESSI</sup></strong><strong><sup>VE</sup></strong><strong><sup> TRAINING</sup></strong></span><strong><sup><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">&nbsp;</span><br /></sup></strong></span></span><br /><sup><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Hypopressives is a revolutionary whole body system of training using breathing and postural techniques to create positive changes in the core, pelvic floor and posture.&nbsp;</span></sup><sup><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">You would benefit from it if you wish to PREVENT or TREAT any of the following:<br /></span></sup><br /><sup><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">INCONTINENCE</span></sup><b