                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           (190915, 0, 'Botox Hyperhidrosis Recall 4 months', 'Your Next Treatment', '<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n</head>\n<body>\n<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 1\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"blob:https://crm.pabau.com/abc77137-e364-47d9-8d88-68323c821684\" alt=\"page1image392\" width=\"450.959990\" height=\"131.280000\" />\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\n<div class=\"column\">\n<p>Dear&nbsp;[APPOINTMENTFIRSTNAME],<br /><br />We hope you\'re well and that your&nbsp;Hyperhidrosis treatment with us was effective. We normally recommend a maintenance treatment every 4-6 months. It has now been 4 months since your last treatment with us. If you haven\'t already booked your next appointment, would you like to do so now? <br /><br />If you would like to make a booking, you can:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Call: 07718219145</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Email: info@drtatiana.co.uk</p>\n</li>\n<li>Book online: <a href=\"http://www.drtatiana.co.uk\">www.drtatiana.co.uk</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><br />We hope to see you again soon. <br /><br />Kind Regards,</p>\n<p>Dr Tatiana &amp; Team<br />[COMPANYSTREET]<br />[COMPANYCITY]<br />[COMPANYPOSTAL]</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>', 0, 'email', '2018-10-26 00:45:12', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, '', '', 0, 'general', '', '', 0, 0),
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           (192652, 0, 'Laser CO2 *LIGHT* treatment recall 6 weeks ', 'Hi, is it time for your next CO2 laser treatment? ', '<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n</head>\n<body>\n<div class=\"page\" style=\"text-align: center;\" title=\"Page 1\"><img src=\"https://crm.pabau.com/cdn/template_archive/4627/template_attachments/f4d88d4d18a550388b7f092fec068b3f.png\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n<br />\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\n<div class=\"column\">\n<p>Dear&nbsp;[APPOINTMENTFIRSTNAME],<br /><br />I&nbsp;hope you\'re well. I hope you enjoyed your mini-CO2 Laser treatment with us and are seeing some improvement of your skin quality. I normally recommend having a course of treatments to achieve optimal skin results. It has been 6 weeks since your last treatment with us so I wanted to get in touch to see if you&nbsp;would like to book your next treatment session. Please feel free to get in touch, my team&nbsp;and I would be very happy to help.</p>\n<p><br />If you would like a review appointment, you can:&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Call: 07718219145</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Email: info@drtatiana.co.uk</p>\n</li>\n<li>Book online: www.drtatiana.co.uk</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br />We hope to see you again soon.&nbsp;<br /><br />Kind Regards,</p>\n<p>Dr Tatiana &amp; Team<br />[COMPANYSTREET]<br />[COMPANYCITY]<br />[COMPANYPOSTAL]</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>', 0, 'email', '2018-11-09 06:51:31', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, '', '', 0, 'general', '', '', 0, 0),
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           (192859, 0, 'Vitamin A (Retinol/Tretinoin) Topical Aftercare ', 'Information about your Vitamin A cream', '<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n</head>\n<body>\n<img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://crm.pabau.com/cdn/template_archive/4627/template_attachments/527566e1629e97e9154356c419513a6c.JPG\" alt=\"\" /><strong>About Vitamin A/Retinol/Tretinoin&nbsp;cream&nbsp;</strong><br /><br /><br /><br />Thank you for your treatment with Dr Tatiana Aesthetic Clinic. We hope you had a great experience. To make sure you get the most from your treatment, we are sending you some aftercare tips. Vitamin A (also known as retinol&nbsp;or&nbsp;tretinoin) is <strong>one of the&nbsp;best ingredients</strong>&nbsp;you can use to improve many aspects of your skin. Vitamin A cream is used to improve skin texture, pigmentation, acne, rosacea, sun damage and signs of ageing. Vitamin A cream comes in various strengths and concentrations; some are available to buy from a store or online (less potent) and some are available only by prescription (more potent). <br /><br />At the Dr Tatiana Aesthetic Clinic, we often use the following formulations of Vitamin A:&nbsp;<br />\n<ul>\n<li>ZO Retinol&nbsp;wrinkle and texture repair 0.5% and 1%</li>\n<li>ZO Retinol&nbsp;skin brightener 0.5% and 1%</li>\n<li>Tretinoin&nbsp;0.025%&nbsp;</li>\n<li>Tretinoin&nbsp;0.05% (Ketrel)</li>\n<li>Tretinoin&nbsp;0.1% (Retirides)</li>\n</ul>\n<br />Whilst Vitamin A creams have a huge number of benefits for the skin, they also have some side-effects. These include:&nbsp;<br />\n<ul>\n<li>Redness</li>\n<li>Sensitvity</li>\n<li>Dryness and Peeling</li>\n<li>Tightness&nbsp;</li>\n<li>Itching</li>\n<li>Pimples or breakouts</li>\n</ul>\n&nbsp;<br />These are normal and settle over the first few weeks as you skin begins to tolerate Vitamin A better. To minimise these side-effects we normally recommend the following:&nbsp;<br />\n<ul>\n<li>For the first 2-3 weeks, use Vitamin A on alternate nights (not every night).&nbsp;</li>\n<li>Initially, keep a margin of 1-2cm away from eyes and mouth. As the skin gains better tolerance, you can begin to dab small amounts of cream around the eyes and mouth.&nbsp;</li>\n<li>Avoid using Vitamin A on the neck.&nbsp;</li>\n<li>Use a colloid moisturiser like ZO Revitatrol&nbsp;as this is very calming for the skin and does not aggravate acne. This helps with the sensitivity, dryness, tightness and itching.&nbsp;</li>\n<li>You can take an antihistamine tablet if the skin feels uncomfortably itchy. For example: loratadine&nbsp;or cetirizine (non-drowsy options).&nbsp;</li>\n<li>Try your best to persist with the treatment plan, as things do get better as your skin begins to understand and tolerate the vitamin A better.&nbsp;</li>\n</ul>\n<br />Whilst vitamin A is an excellent skincare ingredient, it is not suitable in some circumstances or the treatment plan may need to be adjusted:<br />\n<ul>\n<li>If you are pregnant or trying for a pregnancy&nbsp;</li>\n<li>If you are breastfeeding&nbsp;</li>\n<li>If you are currently undergoing Isotretinoin&nbsp;(Roaccutane) therapy.&nbsp;</li>\n<li>If you are currently undergoing a course of Laser/IPL hair removal.&nbsp;</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br />We hope this information is useful for you. Please get in touch if you have any questions, we would be very happy to help.&nbsp;<br /><br />You can:&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Call: 07718219145&nbsp;</li>\n<li>Email: <a href=\"mailto:info@drtatiana.co.uk\">info@drtatiana.co.uk</a>&nbsp;</li>\n<li>Book appointments online: <a href=\"http://www.drtatiana.co.uk\">www.drtatiana.co.uk</a>&nbsp;</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong><br />Leave us a review</strong><br />We would love a review on your experience with us. It is so important for potential clients to know what you thought of your experience and it also helps us to know what we&rsquo;re doing well and what we could improve, so please take a minute to give us your feedback! :&nbsp;<a href=\"http://search.google.com/local/writereview?placeid=ChIJ-2fQhNQadkgR-BvD3hTY1OM\">http://search.google.com/local/writereview?placeid=ChIJ-2fQhNQadkgR-BvD3hTY1OM</a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Follow us on&nbsp;Instagram</strong><br />We are very active on social media. There are lots of before/after pictures, skin tips and video&nbsp;blogs&nbsp;from Dr Tatiana and her team. Please follow us on&nbsp;Instagram&nbsp;@dr_tatiana_clinic</p>\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<p>With Kind Regards,</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Dr Tatiana and the Team<br />35 Devonshire Place<br />London, W1G&nbsp;<br /><br /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n</body>\n</html>', 0, 'email', '2018-11-09 15:17:12', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, '', '', 0, 'aftercare', '', '', 0, 0),
