ss=\"mcnTextBlock\" style=\"min-width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; mso-table-lspace: 0pt; mso-table-rspace: 0pt; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\" border=\"0\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody class=\"mcnTextBlockOuter\">\n<tr>\n<td class=\"mcnTextBlockInner\" style=\"padding-top: 9px; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\" valign=\"top\"><br />\n<table class=\"mcnTextContentContainer\" style=\"max-width: 100%; min-width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; mso-table-lspace: 0pt; mso-table-rspace: 0pt; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\" border=\"0\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" align=\"left\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"mcnTextContent\" style=\"mso-line-height-rule: exactly; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; word-break: break-word; color: #606060; font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 15px; line-height: 150%; text-align: left; padding: 0 18px 9px 18px;\" valign=\"top\"><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: helvetica neue,helvetica,arial,verdana,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Thank you once again for visiting the clinic today for your appointment with&nbsp;[AWITH]. We really hope you enjoyed your experience here with us.</span></span></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: helvetica neue,helvetica,arial,verdana,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><br />Included below are our post treatment recommendations, which will help you achieve optimum results from your procedure. We hope you find these helpful, but as always, if you have any further queries or concerns, please don\'t hesitate to contact our friendly team who are always on hand and happy to help.&nbsp;</span></span></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: helvetica neue,helvetica,arial,verdana,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">In the meantime, we would be hugely grateful if you could spare a moment to share your experience and feedback with us. This feedback is invaluable to us in ensuring we are delivering the exceptional standards of client care that our customers except and deserve. To thank you for your time we will automatically enter you in to our monthly prize draw for the chance to win a &pound;50 face etc medispa&nbsp;gift card. To leave a review, simply click the button beneath the aftercare information, below.<br /><br />Thank you once again, we look forward to welcoming you to the clinic again soon</span></span></div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<br /><br /><!-- [if mso]><br /> </td><br /> <![endif]--> <!-- [if mso]><br /> </tr><br /> </table><br /> <![endif]--></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<br />\n<table class=\"mcnImageBlock\" style=\"min-width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; mso-table-lspace: 0pt; mso-table-rspace: 0pt; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\" border=\"0\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody class=\"mcnImageBlockOuter\">\n<tr>\n<td class=\"mcnImageBlockInner\" style=\"padding: 9px; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\" valign=\"top\"><img src=\"https://crm.pabau.com/cdn/template_archive/5617/template_attachments/663f2bbf607afe4efe40f7707dd9ac5c.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"594\" height=\"396\" /></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<table class=\"mcnTextBlock\" style=\"min-width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; mso-table-lspace: 0pt; mso-table-rspace: 0pt; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\" border=\"0\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody class=\"mcnTextBlockOuter\">\n<tr>\n<td class=\"mcnTextBlockInner\" style=\"padding-top: 9px; text-size-adjust: 100%; text-align: center;\" valign=\"top\"><br />\n<table class=\"mcnTextContentContainer\" style=\"max-width: 100%; min-width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; mso-table-lspace: 0pt; mso-table-rspace: 0pt; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\" border=\"0\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" align=\"left\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"mcnTextContent\" style=\"mso-line-height-rule: exactly; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; word-break: break-word; color: #606060; font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 15px; line-height: 150%; text-align: left; padding: 0 18px 9px 18px;\" valign=\"top\">\n<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 1\">\n<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 1\">\n<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 1\">\n<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 1\">\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\n<div class=\"column\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<p><strong>Dermal Filler Aftercare Information<br /></strong></p>\n<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 1\">\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\n<div class=\"column\">\n<p>Every member of our clinic is committed to your satisfaction with the care you received today. It is important you feel that we have listened to, and responded to, all of your questions and concerns. Please do not hesitate to ask your clinician any questions you may have regarding your treatment today, and the steps you will need to take in the coming days to assure the results of your treatment meet your expectations. The following information will assist you in maximising your results, and minimising any potential complications from your treatment.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p><strong>Aftercare Advice</strong></p>\n<p>To ensure the best possible outcome of your treatment you should be sure to take the following precautions:</p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li>\n<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 1\">\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\n<div class=\"column\">\n<p>Following your treatment, you may be red and slightly bruised at the site of injection. This may last up to 7 days, but can normally be easily disguised using concealer make up.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 1\">\n<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 1\">\n<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 1\">\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\n<div class=\"column\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li>\n<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 1\">\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\n<div class=\"column\">\n<p>If you have had a dental block you may remain numb for a short period of time following treatment, which can make the area feel more swollen.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 1\">\n<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 1\">\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\n<div class=\"column\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li>You should avoid touching the treated area for 6 hours. This allows the small needle holes to close up thereby preventing infection.&nbsp;</li>\n<li>\n<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 1\">\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\n<div class=\"column\">\n<p>Swelling is unusual, but injections into the lips do tend to swell more than other areas and could take up to 3 days to resolve. It is not advised for the first 24 hours, but after this period anti inflammatory medication can be used for any swelling. Cold packs will also help to reduce swelling.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</li>\n<li>It is recommended that you do not use any makeup for 12 hours following the treatment. This includes applying any creams to the lips following lip augmentation.<br /><br /></li>\n<li>Do not expose the treated areas to extreme heat (eg sun beds and saunas) for 2 weeks post treatment. Avoid extended exposure to direct sunlight, UV rays and temperatures below 0&deg;, until any redness and swelling has resolved.<br /><br /></li>\n<li>If you have suffered from cold sores, the treatment may result in a fresh eruption of the virus. If this occurs, you do not need to seek medical advice, you may use Zovirax&nbsp;cream.<br /><br /></li>\n<li>If you are taking aspiring, high doses of vitamin C or any other anti-coagulants the risk of bruising and bleeding may be higher. Discuss any concerns with us.&nbsp;<br /><br /></li>\n<li>Following lip augmentation, the lips may feel tender and injected filler may appear uneven- this will gradually resolve itself within the first week and will not usually effect the final result.</li>\n<li>\n<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 1\">\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\n<div class=\"column\">\n<p>Due to the nature of dermal fillers, they draw water into the complex, and for the first few days can feel a little lumpy. Simple massage will disperse any water that has collected and help the filler integrate into the tissues.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</li>\n<li>To reduce the risk of infection do not touch the area that has been treated for 6 hours, and after this time make sure that your hands are clean prior to touching.&nbsp;</li>\n<li>\n<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 1\">\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\n<div class=\"column\">\n<p>Patients can be allergic to dermal fillers. This is a rare but very serious complication. If you experience swelling you think is abnormal, or are suffering from an allergic reaction, contact our clinical team immediately using the contact numbers below.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</li>\n<li>Use pain medication where required and in accordance with your practitioners recommendations.&nbsp;<br /><br /></li>\n<li>Do not schedule and face-down massage or dental work immediately following treatment.<br /><br /></li>\n<li>Arnica&nbsp;can be used to reduce bruising.&nbsp;<br /><br /></li>\n<li>No smoking (or kissing following lip augmentation) on the day of treatment.&nbsp;<br /><br /></li>\n<li>Apply ice as required for up to 24 hours.<br /><br /></li>\n<li>Avoid sleeping on the treated area for 2 days.&nbsp;<br /><br /></li>\n<li>Do not expose the treated area to intense facial treatments for 1 week after treatment.<br /><br /></li>\n<li>For your well-being and aesthetic satisfaction, please consult with your practitioner about any follow up appointments required.&nbsp;</li>\n<li>\n<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 1\">\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\n<div class=\"column\">\n<p>In the rare event of an accidental injection of the product into a small artery, or pressure on a vessel from the injection occurs, an arterial occlusion can result. If you experience increasing pain in the area of injection, or blanching or blueness of the skin, these could be signs of an occlusion. Should this happen, or you are concerned it may be happening, contact our clinical team at once using the details found below.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\nContact the clinic immediately if you develop any signs or symptoms of necrosis such as excruciating&nbsp;pain, whitened/grey area of skin or mottled red skin.&nbsp;<br /><br />Contact medical advice immediately if you experience difficulty in breathing/swallowing/speaking. If you develop hives, swelling of the face or throat, wheezing or feeling faint. These are possible symptoms of a severe allergic reaction.</div>\n<div class=\"column\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"column\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Further Treatment</strong></div>\n<div class=\"column\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"column\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">How long the effect of Dermal Filler lasts is dependent on the individual. There are many factors to consider, such as the structure of the skin, your lifestyle and age. Your filler should last 6 to 12 months, and regular treatments will maintain optimum results. You will be advised if a follow up appointment is necessary following your treatment.</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<br /><!-- [if mso]><br /> </td><br /> <![endif]--> <!-- [if mso]><br /> </tr><br /> </table><br /> <![endif]--></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<br />\n<table class=\"mcnButtonBlock\" style=\"min-width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; mso-table-lspace: 0pt; mso-table-rspace: 0pt; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\" border=\"0\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody class=\"mcnButtonBlockOuter\">\n<tr>\n<td class=\"mcnButtonBlockInner\" style=\"mso-line-height-rule: exactly; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; padding: 0 18px 18px 18px;\" align=\"center\" valign=\"top\"><br />\n<table class=\"mcnButtonContentContainer\" style=\"border-collapse: separate !important; border-radius: 3px; background-color: #e0c2c2; mso-table-lspace: 0pt; mso-table-rspace: 0pt; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"mcnButtonContent\" style=\"font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; padding: 15px; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\" align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">Leave a <a href=\"https://uk.trustpilot.com/review/faceetcmedispa.co.uk\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">TrustPilot</span></a>&nbsp;review</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<br />\n<table class=\"mcnFollowBlock\" style=\"min-width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; mso-table-lspace: 0pt; mso-table-rspace: 0pt; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\" border=\"0\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody class=\"mcnFollowBlockOuter\">\n<tr>\n<td class=\"mcnFollowBlockInner\" style=\"padding: 9px; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\" align=\"center\" valign=\"top\"><br />\n<table class=\"mcnFollowContentContain