                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           (220627, 0, 'initial booking confirmed', 'initial booking confirmed', '<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n</head>\n<body>\n<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Dear &nbsp;<strong>[CLIENTSALUTATION] [APPOINTMENTFIRSTNAME] [APPOINTMENTLASTNAME],</strong><br /><br />We are pleased to&nbsp;have booked your appointment with Dr Dev Shah - Dermatology Consultant and Skin Surgeon at :</span><br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>[ASTARTTIME] on&nbsp;[AWEEKDAY], [ADATE] in&nbsp;[ALOCATIONNAME],[ALOCATIONADDRESS2] [ALOCATIONPOSTAL].&nbsp;<br /><br /><br />An appointment reminder email will be sent nearer the time.<br /><br /></strong></span></span>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Best wishes</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Ms&nbsp;Bina&nbsp;Shanti&nbsp;- Private Secretary to&nbsp;Dr Dev&nbsp;Shah -&nbsp;&nbsp;Telephone: 07453164488&nbsp; Email:&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:office@drdevshah.com\">office@drdevshah.com</a>&nbsp; Website :&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.drdevshah.com\" target=\"_blank\">drdevshah.com&nbsp;</a></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;<br /><br /></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Dr Shah also provides services at the following hospitals, please click on the \'map\' links for directions:&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><em><strong>BMI&nbsp;Bishopswood&nbsp;Hospital</strong></em>,&nbsp;Northwood, London. HA6 2JW.&nbsp; &nbsp;Call :&nbsp;01923 835 814&nbsp;<a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/iSFMqWuRtwcjXWuHA\">Map&nbsp;</a></span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><em><strong>BMI&nbsp;Chiltern,</strong></em>&nbsp;Great&nbsp;Missenden. HP16 0EN. Call:&nbsp;01494 890890&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/iD8pZstuVBw\">Map&nbsp;</a></span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><em><strong>OneStopDoctors</strong></em>,&nbsp;Boundary Way,&nbsp;Hemel&nbsp;Hempstead&nbsp;HP2 7YU. Call:&nbsp;01442 331900&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/uyyA65nqQRT2\">Map</a>&nbsp;</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><em><strong>Spire&nbsp;Bushey&nbsp;Diagnostic Centre,</strong></em>&nbsp;290 Centennial Ave,&nbsp;Elstree,&nbsp;&nbsp;WD6 3SU.&nbsp; Call:&nbsp;020 8736 4608&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/QMPitrc1QBu\">Map</a></span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><em><strong>Amersham&nbsp;Hospital,</strong></em>&nbsp;Dermatology Department, Entrance 1,&nbsp;Whielden&nbsp;St,&nbsp;Amersham&nbsp;HP7 0JD, Call: 01494 734616 &nbsp;<a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/5eH8RwUdMfmPAFZb7\">Map</a></span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></div>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>TO GET THE BEST out of your appointment with Dr Shah please check the following before attending:</strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">REFERRAL LETTER &ndash; please bring a referral letter with you, if you have one. Alternatively you can email this to us at&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:office@drdevshah.com\">office@drdevshah.com</a></span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">PREVIOUS HISTORY &ndash; please bring a list of your medications and past medical history &ndash; if you do not have one, please bring the actual medications with you in a bag.</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">ASK YOUR GP PRACTICE - if you are unsure about your past medical history and previous diagnoses please ask your GP surgery for summary of your records &ndash; this is generally free</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">PHOTOS - take photos of your rash or lesion before coming and then bring the photos with you, this will help with your diagnosis if your rash or lesion has resolved or changes</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">FAMILY - bring a family member or friend to help in the consultation</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">LIST - Dr Shah is happy to answer your list of questions to help direct the consultation&nbsp;</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><strong><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">COSTS&nbsp;INVOLVED</span><br /></strong></span></strong></span></span>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">My fee for an initial consultation will not exceed&nbsp;<strong>&pound;250&nbsp;</strong>and my fee for any follow-up consultation will not exceed&nbsp;<strong>&pound;200</strong>.&nbsp; These estimates are correct as of the date of this letter.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">If there are any FURTHER fees which I or the hospital will charge in relation to any of the tests I advise that you have, I will let you know what those will be.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Private Medical Insurance</span></strong></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">If you have private medical insurance, please contact your insurer before your consultation, to check the terms of your policy, particularly the level and type of outpatient cover you have, including any reimbursement limits on individual consultation fees. Please note you are responsible for any fees not covered by your insurer.</span></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Financial Interests</span></strong></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">I am legally obliged to tell you if I have any financial interests in&nbsp;<strong>[ALOCATIONNAME]</strong>&nbsp;or any equipment there.&nbsp; I can confirm I do not have any such financial interests.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n</body>\n</html>', 0, 'email', '2019-05-23 09:33:28', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, '', '', 0, 'confirmation', '', '', 0, 1);
