![endif]-->\n<table class=\"mcnTextContentContainer\" style=\"max-width: 100%; min-width: 100%;\" border=\"0\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" align=\"left\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"mcnTextContent\" style=\"padding: 0 18px 9px 18px;\" valign=\"top\"><span style=\"font-size: 10px;\">&copy; 2020 Maison Lut&eacute;tia<br /> 6 rue Amp&egrave;re 75017 Paris&nbsp; I&nbsp; +33156900828<br /> <a href=\"https://www.maisonlutetia.com/fr/politique-de-protection-de-la-vie-privee-lutetia/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Politique de protection de la vie priv&eacute;e</span></a> I <a href=\"https://www.maisonlutetia.com/fr/mentions-legales\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Mentions L&eacute;gales</span></a></span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<!-- [if mso]>\n				</td>\n				<![endif]--> <!-- [if mso]>\n				</tr>\n				</table>\n				<![endif]--></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<!-- [if (gte mso 9)|(IE)]>\n                                    </td>\n                                    </tr>\n                                    </table>\n                                    <![endif]--></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<!-- // END TEMPLATE --></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</center>\n</body>\n</html>', 0, 'email', '2019-07-18 14:14:53', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, '', '', 0, 'leads', '', '', 0, 1),
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           (223743, 0, 'Microneedling', 'Microneedling', '<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n</head>\n<body>\n<p><strong>Microneedling&nbsp;and RRS&nbsp;Mesotherapy Aftercare</strong><br /><br /></p>\n<p>Do not use any AHA\'s, BHA\'s or Retinol on your skin for 24-36 hours or advised by your skin-care professional</p>\n<p><br />It is imperative that you use a sunscreen with an SPF of at least 30 and avoid direct sunlight for at least a month.</p>\n<p><br />Patients with hypersensitivity to the sun should take extra precautions to guard against exposure immediately following the procedure.<br /><br /></p>\n<p>DO NOT PICK OR PULL THE SKIN. Any redness will decrease over 24-36 hours</p>\n<p><br />When washing your face, do not scrub. Use a cleanser designed for sensitive skins.</p>\n<p><br />Apply a light moisturizer,&nbsp;chiroxy as often as needed to relieve dryness and tightness.</p>\n<p><br />Do not have any other facial treatment for at least two weeks after your&nbsp;treatment.<br /><br /></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Microdermabrasion&nbsp;Post Treatment Advice</span></span></strong></h1>\n<h3><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>After Treatment</strong></span></h3>\n<div>After treatment it is expected that your skin may look pink or red. This will&nbsp;decrease dramatically over 24 to 36 hours after treatment.</div>\n<h3><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>What to do after treatment</strong></span></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Please do not wear your normal make up&nbsp;on the day of treatment with the exception of&nbsp;Oxygenetix&nbsp;or other post procedure make-up</li>\n<li>On the evening of your treatment you may gently wash your face and use gentle&nbsp;skincare products</li>\n<li>Always wear a broad spectrum, high factor sun protection (SPF&nbsp;30-50) on the face, neck,&nbsp;d&eacute;colletage&nbsp;and hands</li>\n<li>Results are always best with courses of treatment. These can be performed every 3 weeks if desired.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>What NOT to do after treatment</strong></span>&nbsp;</h3>\n<div>\n<ul>\n<li>Avoid using any strong active skincare ingredients (like&nbsp;glycolic&nbsp;acid or&nbsp;retinol) for 3 days after treatment</li>\n<li>No strenuous exercise, saunas, steam rooms or sunbathing for 24 hours after treatment</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<h3><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>What to watch out for after treatment</strong></span></h3>\n<div>\n<ul>\n<li>You may experience some gentle skin flaking. Do not pick at this as picking can cause irritation, scarring and&nbsp;hyperpigmentation.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div><strong><strong>Please ensure you discuss your overall treatment programme with your practitioner as this will enable you to receive the best results from treatment. Illuminate Skin Clinic also offers professional skin care advice and stocks many&nbsp;cosmeceutical&nbsp;products which will help you to enhance your outcome. We also offer dermal fillers, facial contouring, lip shaping, skin peels, fat dissolving injections,&nbsp;CoolSculpting, thread lifts,&nbsp;PRP&nbsp;and&nbsp;microneedling. For more information please&nbsp;email&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:hello@illuminateskinclinic.co.uk\">hello@illuminateskinclinic.co.uk</a>&nbsp;or call us on 0330 133 1272</strong></strong></div>\n</body>\n</html>', 0, 'email', '2019-07-22 18:29:21', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, '', '', 0, 'aftercare', '', '', 0, 0);
