                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           (224332, 0, 'CO2 Laser Information', 'CO2 Laser at the Dr Tatiana Clinic', '<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n</head>\n<body>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; line-height: 100%;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h3 class=\"western\"><br /><br />Hello,</h3>\n<p>Thank you for your enquiry about CO2 Laser treatments.</p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; line-height: 100%;\" align=\"justify\"><span lang=\"en-GB\">The CO2 laser has long been established as a safe and effective treatment for acne scars, traumatic scars, pigmentation, sun damage, melasma, enlarged pores, fine lines and uneven skin texture. The treatment is best suited to light to olive skin types. In some cases, darker skin types may be suitable for the treatment. The principle of skin resurfacing is to stimulate the skin&rsquo;s natural healing process to replace damaged skin with fresh, healthy, new skin.<br /><br />Laser skin resurfacing works by creating small areas of trauma in the skin; the injured skin then repairs and creates new collagen, elastin and skin hydrators. This process converts scarred, uneven or porous skin into healthy skin. Within safe limits, a greater injury will stimulate greater remodelling of the tissue. <br /><br />Carbon dioxide (CO2) laser resurfacing is the gold standard treatment for skin resurfacing. CO2 laser can be a fully ablative treatment (i.e. all of the skin is treated) or fractional ablative treatment (i.e. pin-point areas of the skin are treated). The fully-ablative method is very effective but requires a longer recovery; the fractional ablative method has a faster recovery but may require several sessions to achieve optimal results. At the Dr Tatiana Clinic, we offer a comprehensive range of CO2 laser treatments.</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; line-height: 100%;\" align=\"justify\"><span lang=\"en-GB\"><strong><br />What area can be treated with th CO2 laser?:</strong><br /><br />The most frequent areas to be treated with CO2 laser are face, neck, <span data-dobid=\"hdw\">d&eacute;colletage</span> and hands.<br /></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; line-height: 100%;\" align=\"justify\"><span lang=\"en-GB\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<div class=\"modal-header\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div id=\"before-after-carousel\" class=\"carousel slide\" data-ride=\"carousel\" data-interval=\"false\">\n<div class=\"carousel-inner\">\n<div class=\"carousel-item active\">\n<div class=\"container-fluid\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-8 offset-2 col-sm-6 offset-sm-0 col-md-5 offset-md-1\">\n<div class=\"card card-inverse before\"><img class=\"card-img-top\" src=\"https://www.drtatiana.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/lsr-01-before.jpg\" alt=\"Laser Skin Resurfacing - Before 01\" />&nbsp; <img class=\"card-img-top\" src=\"https://www.drtatiana.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/lsr-01-after.jpg\" alt=\"Laser Skin Resurfacing - After 01\" /><br />\n<h3 class=\"card-title text-center\">Before&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; After</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p><strong>What to expect</strong>:</p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; line-height: 100%;\" align=\"justify\"><span lang=\"en-GB\">All our laser treatments require a consultation prior to full treatment. This enables you to ask any questions you may have, prepare your skin for the treatment and to try the laser out, so that you know what to expect during your treatment and recovery. The patch-test also enables us to identify which laser settings will work best for you. We recommend stopping retinol 5 days prior and avoiding sun exposure 4 weeks prior patch-test. </span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; line-height: 100%;\" align=\"justify\"><span lang=\"en-GB\">On the day of your treatment your therapist will help you through the consent form and take photographs of the area to be treated. The therapist will clean the skin (so don&rsquo;t worry if you have makeup on) and apply numbing cream which will be left on for around 30-40 minutes. The doctor will then clean the skin and administer numbing injections to ensure that your treatment is pain-free and comfortable. Special protective goggles are then placed over the eyes. <br /></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; line-height: 100%;\" align=\"justify\"><span lang=\"en-GB\">The treatment is then carried out. This takes approximately 30 minutes and is usually completely pain-free with injection anaesthetic. During the treatment you should feel comfortable and relaxed; you can talk to the team or listen to music. <br /><br /></span></p>\n<p><strong>After the treatment:<br /> </strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; line-height: 100%;\" align=\"justify\"><span lang=\"en-GB\">After the treatment we will cool the skin, apply a soothing cream and then place you under the LED mask for approximately 20 minutes to help reduce skin inflammation and optimise skin repair. In general, the skin may feel hot, be mildly swollen and will have some white or brown crusts across the surface. We provide you with special aftercare skin products to use including a face wash, healing cream and sunblock. In some cases, we may also give you antibiotic cream or tablets and/or antiviral tablets to prevent risk of infection. <br />During the recovery, you wil experience some redness, swelling, sensitivity and crusting of the skin. Most people can be back to work within 5 days and back to normal social activities within 7 days. With more intense treatments, the recovery may be a little longer. </span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in;\"><strong>How many sessions are required?:&nbsp;<br /> </strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in;\"><span lang=\"en-GB\">For optimal results, most patients will require 1-3 sessions (approximately 1 session per month). In some circumstances, more sessions may be needed.<br /></span><strong><br /> When will I see results?:&nbsp;<br /> </strong>Initial results are seen approximately one month after the CO2 treatment, you will notice your skin to be visibly smoother, healthier and younger looking. Results will continue to improve over the next 6 months.<br /><br /><strong>How much does it cost?:<br /><br /></strong></p>\n<table width=\"418\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border: none; padding: 0in;\" width=\"345\">\n<p><strong>Area</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border: none; padding: 0in;\" width=\"73\">\n<p><strong>Price in &pound;</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border: none; padding: 0in;\" width=\"345\">\n<p>Full face resurfacing</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border: none; padding: 0in;\" width=\"73\">\n<p>2500</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border: none; padding: 0in;\" width=\"345\">\n<p>Full face and&nbsp;<span data-dobid=\"hdw\">d&eacute;colletage</span> resurfacing</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border: none; padding: 0in;\" width=\"73\">\n<p>3500</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border: none; padding: 0in;\" width=\"345\">\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.2in;\">Full face and PLEXR Blepharoplasty</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border: none; padding: 0in;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"73\">\n<p>3500</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p><br /> <em>*Please note that a deposit of &pound;50 is required in order to secure your treatment appointment with the balance&nbsp;paid on the day of treatment. We do not offer any payment plans.</em>&nbsp;<br /> <em>** Please note that we request at least 48 hours notice for any cancellations or rescheduling appointments. If you are unable to provide at least 48 hours notice, your deposit will be forfeited.&nbsp;</em><br /> <strong><br /> Do you have any questions?<br /> </strong>We are here to make your treatment&nbsp;easy, comfortable and safe. If there&rsquo;s anything we can do to make sure you have an&nbsp;exceptional experience&nbsp;with us, please do let us know.</p>\n<p><strong>Kind Regards,</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Dr Tatiana and Team</strong>&nbsp;<br /> <br /> Bookings: +447718219145<br /> Email:&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:info@drtatiana.co.uk\">info@drtatiana.co.uk</a><br /> <br /> Dr Tatiana Aesthetic Dermatology Clinic<br /> 35&nbsp;Devonshire&nbsp;Place, London, W1G 6JP<br /> <a href=\"http://www.drtatiana.co.uk/\">www.drtatiana.co.uk</a>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; line-height: 100%;\">&nbsp;</p>\n</body>\n</html>', 0, 'email', '2019-08-04 11:59:12', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, '', '', 0, 'general', '', '', 0, 0);
INSERT INTO `message_templates` (`template_id`, `company_id`, `template_name`, `subject`, `message`, `created_by`, `template_type`, `created_at`, `date_changed_at`, `template_sub_type`, `template_sub_type_service`, `parent_id`, `header`, `footer`, `exclude_margins`, `template_group`, `subtype_letter`, `word_template`, `is_default`, `folder_id`) VALUES
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           (224404, 0, 'Facials Information', 'Facials at the Dr Tatiana Clinic', '<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n</head>\n<body>\n<h3><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://crm.pabau.com/cdn/template_archive/4627/template_attachments/16016910b65e372386428e425212b374.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"687\" height=\"200\" /></h3>\n<h3>Hello,</h3>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; line-height: 100%;\" align=\"justify\">Thank you for your enquiry about facials. <span lang=\"en-GB\">At the Dr Tatiana Clinic, we offer a number of evidence-based facial treatments that give long-term improvements in skin health. Our facials work to treat acne and scars, reduce pigmentation, smooth the skin texture, minimise pores and hydrate the skin. At your first consultation with one of our skin experts, we will assess the skin and create a tailored skin programme to address your skin needs. </span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; line-height: 100%;\" align=\"justify\"><span lang=\"en-GB\"><strong><br />Our skin treatments include: </strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; line-height: 100%;\" align=\"justify\"><span lang=\"en-GB\">Profound skin tightening <a href=\"https://www.drtatiana.co.uk/treatments/profound-rf\">(link to Profound)</a><br /></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; line-height: 100%;\" align=\"justify\"><span lang=\"en-GB\">Microneedling <a href=\"https://www.drtatiana.co.uk/treatments/facials/microneedling\">(link to microneedling)</a><br /></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; line-height: 100%;\" align=\"justify\"><span lang=\"en-GB\">Mesotherapy <a href=\"https://www.drtatiana.co.uk/treatments/facials/mesotherapy\">(link to mesotherapy)</a><br /></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; line-height: 100%;\" align=\"justify\"><span lang=\"en-GB\">Biorevitalisation <a href=\"https://www.drtatiana.co.uk/treatments/facials/biorevitalisation\">(link to biorevitalisation)</a><br /></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; line-height: 100%;\" align=\"justify\"><span lang=\"en-GB\">Platelet-Rich Plasma <a href=\"https://www.drtatiana.co.uk/treatments/facials/platelet-rich-plasma-prp\">(link to PRP)</a><br /></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; line-height: 100%;\" align=\"justify\"><span lang=\"en-GB\">Dermaplaning (link to dermaplaning)</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; line-height: 100%;\" align=\"justify\"><span lang=\"en-GB\">Extraction (link to extractions)</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; line-height: 100%;\" align=\"justify\"><span lang=\"en-GB\">Chemical peels <a href=\"https://www.drtatiana.co.uk/treatments/facials/chemical-peel\">(link to chemical peel)</a><br /></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; line-height: 100%;\" align=\"justify\"><span lang=\"en-GB\">Laser treatments (link to Laser general page)</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; line-height: 100%;\" align=\"justify\"><span lang=\"en-GB\">LED (link to LED)<br /><br /></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; line-height: 100%;\" align=\"justify\"><span lang=\"en-GB\"><strong>Facials package</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; line-height: 100%;\" align=\"justify\"><span lang=\"en-GB\">To give you better flexibility with your skin treatments and to ensure the optimal treatment for your skin, we have developed a </span><span lang=\"en-GB\"><strong>Bespoke Medi-Facials package</strong></span><span lang=\"en-GB\">. This package consists of a 1-hour tailored facial, every month for 6 months. At each appointment, our therapist will assess your skin and offer you the best combination of treatments for your skin. This can include any combination of chemical peels, extraction, exfoliation, microneedling, mesotherapy, laser, masks and LED. The Bespoke Medi-Facials package is an excellent way of ensuring that every facial is responsive to your skin needs. <br /><br /></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; line-height: 100%;\" align=\"justify\"><span lang=\"en-GB\"><strong>Intravenous Nutrition Therapy</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; line-height: 100%;\" align=\"justify\"><span lang=\"en-GB\">Our facials can also be combined with Intravenous Nutrition Therapy (IVNT) to deliver potent antioxidants, amino acids and vitamins directly into your blood stream. This gradient between the high concentration of nutrients in the blood stream and relatively lower concentration in cells pushes nutrients into your cells. The cells are able to use specific nutrients to improve general health and wellbeing, brighten the skin, enhance mental clarity and energy, boost the immune system and accelerate fat loss. </span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; line-height: 100%;\" align=\"justify\"><span lang=\"en-GB\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><br /><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>IMAGES.....</strong></span><br /><br /><br /><br /><strong><br /><br />What to expect</strong>:</p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; line-height: 100%;\" align=\"justify\"><span lang=\"en-GB\">At your consultation with us, we will assess your skin, discuss your skin concerns and make a treatment plan to address your skin needs. At your treatment appointment, your practitioner will discuss the steps of treatment and take you through the process of consent. We will then clean the skin and take pre-treatment photographs. You will be given a head band and towel to protect your clothing. <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">Where necessary</span>, numbing cream is applied and left on for approximately 20 minutes. The skin is then cleaned and the treatment is started.&nbsp; The treatment takes approximately 20-30 minutes to do. At the end of treatment, the therapist will apply soothing cream and an LED mask. We recommend that you use simple moisturisers and sunblock for 3-5 days after treatment. <br /><br /></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; line-height: 100%;\" align=\"justify\"><span lang=\"en-GB\">We recommend that you pause any treatments like retinol, tretinoin, salicylic acid or glycolic for 5 days prior treatment. </span></p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><strong>After the treatment:<br /></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; line-height: 100%;\" align=\"justify\"><span lang=\"en-GB\">There may be some redness and sensitivity of the skin for 2-3 days after treatment. Most people can continue with normal work and social activities a day after treatment. </span></p>\n<strong><br />How many sessions are required?:&nbsp;<br /></strong>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; line-height: 100%;\" align=\"justify\"><span lang=\"en-GB\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">Depending on the treatment ...</span>For optimal results, most patients will require 4-6 sessions (approximately 1 session a month). </span></p>\n&nbsp;<strong><br />When will I see results?:&nbsp;<br /></strong>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; line-height: 100%;\" align=\"justify\"><span lang=\"en-GB\">Most people will notice that their skin is more vibrant and dewy the day after treatment.</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; line-height: 100%;\" align=\"justify\"><span lang=\"en-GB\">The results of one session will usually last for 1-2 weeks. The results of a course of treatment can last for 3-6 months. We do recommend regular maintenance to maintain optimal results. </span></p>\n&nbsp;<br /><br /><strong>How much does it cost?:</strong><br />\n<table style=\"height: 291px;\" width=\"418\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"524\"><strong>Area</strong></td>\n<td width=\"87\"><strong>Price in &pound;</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Facial - Microdermabrassion (deep clense, exfoliation, ZO brightening mask and LED therapy)</td>\n<td>&nbsp;120</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Facial - Extraction Therapy (deep cleanse, mild acid peel, extraction, anti acne LED)</td>\n<td>&nbsp;150&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Facial - Vitality Treatment (Microdermabrasion, lightmicroneedling with vitamins, hydrating mask, LED) </td>\n<td>&nbsp;150</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Facial - OxyGeneo Facial&nbsp;(exfoliation, infusion of vitamins, hydrating mask, LED)</td>\n<td>&nbsp;150</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Facial - OxyGeneo Facial with Radiofrequency (Exfoliation, Infusion of vitamins, Lymhatic massage and Radiofrequency)</td>\n<td>&nbsp;250</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Legs Facial - Skin lift and tighten (Radiofrequency)</td>\n<td>&nbsp;150<br /><br /></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Facial - Deep skin lift and tighten (Laser with Radiofrequency)</td>\n<td>&nbsp;250</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Skin - Mesotherapy (Vitamin injections, Mask, LED)</td>\n<td>&nbsp;200</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Skin - Vitamin Stimulation treatment (Mesotherapy injections with microneedling, Mask, LED</td>\n<td>&nbsp;350</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Skin - Juvederm Volite Plump for skin hydration</td>\n<td>&nbsp;250<br /><br /></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Skin - Profhilo Skin plump and elasticity treatment</td>\n<td>&nbsp;450</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Skin - Profhilo Skin plump (2 sessions)</td>\n<td>&nbsp;800</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Platelet Reach Plasma (PRP) rejuvenation with vitamins</td>\n<td>&nbsp;600</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Platelet Reach Plasma (PRP) rejuvenation with Hyaluronic acid for hydration</td>\n<td>&nbsp;750</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Facial - Skin Radiance Peel</td>\n<td>&nbsp;150</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Skin - ZO 3 steps (Deep three-acid peel for skin resurfacing, pigmentation and acne treatment)</td>\n<td>&nbsp;450</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Skin - Resurfacing facial (exfoliation, deeper microneedling, hydrating mask aend LED)</td>\n<td>&nbsp;250</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Skin - Complete resurfacing facial (deeper micro needling with acid peel)</td>\n<td>&nbsp;350</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /></div>\n</body>\n</html>', 0, 'email', '2019-08-06 00:26:43', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, '', '', 0, 'general', '', '', 0, 0),
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           (224568, 0, 'How did we do survey (Email)', 'How did we do?', '<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n</head>\n<body>\n<table border=\"0\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\">\n<div align=\"center\">\n<table width=\"600px\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" bgcolor=\"#FFFFFF\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"padding-left: 10px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; text-align: center;\" align=\"left\">\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1><strong><span style=\"font-size: 1.5em;\">How did we do?</span></strong></h1>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">\n<div style=\"border: 1px  solid  #bdbdbd; border-radius: 8px;\">\n<div style=\"padding-left: 10px; font-family: Helvetica,Arial,Verdana,sans-serif;\">\n<h4>Hi [APPOINTMENTNAME],</h4>\n<div style=\"padding-left: 10px;\">Thank you for your recent visit to Our Clinic. We value your feedback very much, and would appreciate if you could take time to fill in our short survey below:</div>\n<div style=\"padding-left: 10px;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div style=\"padding-left: 10px;\">\n<table style=\"font-family: helvetica,Arial,Tahoma,sans-serif;\" width=\"426\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"text-align: left; background-color: #f0f0f0;\"><th style=\"padding-left: 5px;\" colspan=\"2\">\n<table style=\"font-family: helvetica,Arial,Tahoma,sans-serif;\" width=\"426\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"background-color: #f6f6f6; font-size: 14px; color: #333333; width: 400px;\" colspan=\"2\">\n<p>Click below to rate your experience:</p>\n<p><a href=\"[SURVEYLINK]\" target=\"_self\">[SURVEYLINK]</a></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"background-color: #f6f6f6; font-size: 14px; color: #333333; width: 400px;\" colspan=\"2\">&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">\n<p style=\"padding-left: 10px; font-family: Helvetica,Arial,Verdana,sans-serif; color: #999; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 5px;\"><a href=\"https://maps.google.com/maps?q=+[COMPANYSTREET]+,+[COMPANYCITY],+[COMPANYCOUNTRY]\" target=\"_blank\">&nbsp;</a></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p><img style=\"height: 1px; width: 1px; border-width: 0; padding: 0; margin: 0;\" src=\"program/blocked.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" /><img style=\"height: 1px; width: 1px; border-width: 0; padding: 0; margin: 0;\" src=\"program/blocked.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" /></p>\n<div class=\"message-htmlpart\"><!-- html ignored --><!-- head ignored --><!-- meta ignored -->\n<div class=\"rcmBody\" dir=\"auto\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>', 0, 'email', '2019-08-08 15:57:07', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, '', '', 0, 'general', '', '', 0, 1),
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           (224637, 0, 'Platelet-Rich Plasma Information', 'Platelet-Rich Plasma at the Dr Tatiana Clinic', '<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n</head>\n<body>\n<h3><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://crm.pabau.com/cdn/template_archive/4627/template_attachments/16016910b65e372386428e425212b374.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"687\" height=\"200\" />Hello,</h3>\n<p class=\"p1\">Thank you for your enquiry about Platelet-Rich Plasma treatments.</p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; line-height: 100%;\" align=\"justify\"><span lang=\"en-GB\">PRP treatment is the injection of your own blood plasma, that is rich in platelets and fortified with vitamins and nutrients, into the skin. PRP is used to plump and thicken the skin, improve skin tone and texture, reduce signs of ageing and treat pigmentation, scars and stretch-marks. <br /><br />Platelets, within Platelet-Rich Plasma, play a critical role in tissue repair and regeneration. They regulate important steps of the healing process. The injection of PRP stimulates skin repair, therefore tightening, remodelling and plumping the skin. PRP can also be combined with ingredients such as vitamins, minerals, amino acids, nucleic acids, hyaluronic acid and powerful antioxidants such as glutathione. </span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; line-height: 100%;\" align=\"justify\"><span lang=\"en-GB\">PRP is a safe and effective treatment to improve skin texture, acne scars, pigmentation and signs of ageing. The treatment is suitable for all skin types. Due to the use of numbing cream, we do not recommend this treatment during pregnancy or breastfeeding. <br /></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; line-height: 100%;\" align=\"justify\"><span lang=\"en-GB\">We recommend that you pause any treatments like retinol, tretinoin, salicylic acid or glycolic for 5 days prior treatment.</span></p>\n<br />\n<p lang=\"en-GB\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; line-height: 100%;\" align=\"justify\"><strong>What areas can be treated with Platelet-Rich Plasma treatment?:&nbsp;</strong>Most frequent areas to treat with PRP are areas with dull/dry skin, Hyperpigmentation, Hypopigmentation, Melasma, sun damage, wrinkles, acne scars, body scars, stretchmarks, ageing hands and unwanted hair loss.<br /><br /></p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; IMAGES....</span><br />Before&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; After<br /></strong><strong><br />What to expect</strong>:</p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; line-height: 100%;\" align=\"justify\"><span lang=\"en-GB\">At your consultation with us, we will assess your skin, discuss your skin concerns and make a treatment plan to address your skin needs. <br />At your treatment appointment, your practitioner will discuss the steps of treatment and take you through the process of consent. We will then clean the skin and take pre-treatment photographs. You will be given a head band and towel to protect your clothing. Numbing cream is applied and left on for approximately 20 minutes. The skin is then cleaned and the treatment is started. You may feel some mild stinging in the skin, but this is not painful. The treatment takes approximately 20 minutes to do. At the end of treatment, the practitioner will apply soothing cream and an LED mask. The treatment is not painful. Some people may feel a mild stinging sensation during the treatment. </span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; line-height: 100%;\" align=\"justify\"><strong>After the treatment:<br /></strong><span lang=\"en-GB\"><br />There will be some redness, sensitivity and the possibility of some bruises after treatment and this may last for 1-3 days. Most people can continue with normal work and social activities a day after treatment. <br />We recommend that you use simple moisturisers and sunblock for 3-5 days after treatment. <br /></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; line-height: 100%;\" align=\"justify\"><strong><span lang=\"en-GB\">How many sessions are required?:</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span lang=\"en-GB\">For optimal results, most patients will require 4 sessions (approximately 1 session every month).</span><br /><br /><strong>When will I see results?:<br /></strong></p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span lang=\"en-GB\">Most people will notice that their skin is more vibrant and dewy the day after treatment. Improvement in scars, pigmentation or signs of ageing may take several sessions to become apparent. The results of a course of treatment are long-term. We do recommend 1 session every 4-6 months to maintain optimal results.<br /></span><br /><strong>How much does it cost?:</strong></p>\n<div>\n<table style=\"height: 196px;\" width=\"376\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border: none; padding: 0in;\" width=\"345\">\n<p><strong>Area</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border: none; padding: 0in;\" width=\"73\">\n<p><strong>Price per treatment &pound;</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border: none; padding: 0in;\" width=\"345\">\n<p>Platelet-Rich Plasma: </p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border: none; padding: 0in;\" width=\"73\">\n<p>&nbsp;600</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border: none; padding: 0in;\" width=\"345\">\n<p>Platelet-Rich Plasma (PRP) rejuvenation with vitamins</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border: none; padding: 0in;\" width=\"73\">\n<p>&nbsp;600</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border: none; padding: 0in;\" width=\"345\">\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.2in;\">Platelet-Rich Plasma (PRP) rejuvenation with Hyaluronic acid for hydration</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border: none; padding: 0in;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"73\">\n<p>&nbsp;750</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n<em>*Please note that a deposit of &pound;50 is required in order to secure your treatment appointment with the balance&nbsp;paid on the day of treatment. We do not offer any payment plans.</em>&nbsp;<br /><em>** Please note that we request at least 48 hours notice for any cancellations or rescheduling appointments. If you are unable to provide at least 48 hours notice, your deposit will be forfeited.&nbsp;</em><br /><strong><br />Do you have any questions?&nbsp;</strong>We are here to make your treatment&nbsp;easy, comfortable and safe. If there&rsquo;s anything we can do to make sure you have an&nbsp;exceptional experience&nbsp;with us, please do let us know.<br /><br /><strong>Kind Regards,</strong>\n<p class=\"p1\"><strong>Dr Tatiana and Team</strong>&nbsp;<br />Dr Tatiana Aesthetic Dermatology Clinic<br />35&nbsp;Devonshire&nbsp;Place, London, W1G 6JP<br /><a href=\"http://www.drtatiana.co.uk\">www.drtatiana.co.uk</a>&nbsp;<br /><br />Bookings: +447718219145<br />Email:&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:info@drtatiana.co.uk\">info@drtatiana.co.uk</a></p>\n</body>\n</html>', 0, 'email', '2019-08-10 13:25:41', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, '', '', 0, 'general', '', '', 0, 0),
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           (225037, 0, 'SKIN Post Procedure Aftercare', 'Skin Treatment Aftercare Information', '<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n</head>\n<body>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">[COMPANYLOGO_IMG]&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<br /><br /> &nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Skin Treatment&nbsp;<strong>P</strong>ost Procedure Aftercare</span></strong></span></div>\n<br />Dear&nbsp;[APPOINTMENTFIRSTNAME]<br /><br />During your treatment programme please ensure to follow the post procedure aftercare advice given to prevent post treatment complications.<br /><br />After your treatment it is normal to experience redness, minor swelling, tightness, Itching and a scratched appearance to the skin. These common skin reactions will settle within 3-7 days with careful adherence to aftercare.&nbsp;\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\"><br /><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-size: 16px;\"><strong><br />What to do after treatment<br /></strong></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">â˜…</span><span class=\"s2\">&nbsp;Avoid sun beds and direct sun exposure for at least 2 weeks, apply minimum&nbsp;SPF&nbsp;30 daily. Take precautions during summer months and holidays by applying&nbsp;SPF&nbsp;50.</span></p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">â˜…</span><span class=\"s2\">&nbsp;Avoid heat treatments such as saunas, steam rooms, baths and showers for 48 hours.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">â˜…</span><span class=\"s2\">&nbsp;Avoid exfoliation scrubs,&nbsp;AHA&rsquo;s,&nbsp;BHA&rsquo;s, and Vitamin A until the skin has normalised and does not feel sensitive. This can be up to 3-7 days.</span></p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">â˜…</span><span class=\"s2\">&nbsp;Do not pick or pull at flaking skin as this will cause sensitivity and possible pigmentation.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">â˜…</span><span class=\"s2\">&nbsp;Keep skin hydrated and apply the recommended post recovery cream as directed.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">â˜…</span><span class=\"s2\">&nbsp;Avoid strenuous activities exercise, hot yoga and swimming for 48 hours.</span></p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">â˜…</span><span class=\"s2\">&nbsp;Use a clean pillow case on the first evening.<br /><br />â˜… Avoid&nbsp;mobile phone touching skin.<br /></span></p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">â˜…</span><span class=\"s2\">&nbsp;Avoid heavy makeup for 48hours, mineral makeup in recommended, apply with a clean make up brush.</span></p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">â˜…</span><span class=\"s2\">&nbsp;Avoid any other treatments for 2 weeks.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"p1\">In the event of any unexpected side affects such as blistering or persisted heat in the area you must immediately&nbsp;contact the clinic within 24hours.</p>\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\"><br />01925 452745&nbsp;<br /><a href=\"mailto:info@skingenius.co.uk\">info@skingenius.co.uk</a></span></p>\n</body>\n</html>', 0, 'email', '2019-08-21 17:04:49', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, '', '', 0, 'aftercare', '', '', 0, 1),
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           (225039, 0, 'SKIN Post Procedure Aftercare', 'Skin Treatment Aftercare Information', '<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n</head>\n<body>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span class=\"s1\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; [COMPANYLOGO_IMG]<br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</strong></span> <span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-size: 16px;\"><strong>Skin Treatment Post Procedure Aftercare<br /><br /></strong></span><br />Dear&nbsp;[APPOINTMENTFIRSTNAME]</span></p>\n<p class=\"p2\">During your treatment programme please ensure to follow the post procedure aftercare advice given to prevent post treatment complications.</p>\n<p class=\"p2\">After your treatment it is normal to experience redness, minor swelling, hot and tingling sensation and a scratched appearance to the skin, these common skin reactions will settle within 3-7 days with careful adherence to aftercare.&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"p3\"><span class=\"s2\"><br /> </span><span class=\"s1\"><strong><br /> </strong></span><span class=\"s3\"><strong>What to do after treatment</strong></span><span class=\"s1\"><strong><br /> </strong></span></p>\n<p class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s4\">â˜…</span><span class=\"s1\">&nbsp;Avoid sun beds and direct sun exposure for at least 2 weeks, apply minimum&nbsp;SPF&nbsp;30 daily. Take precautions during summer months and holidays by applying&nbsp;SPF&nbsp;50.</span></p>\n<p class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s4\">â˜…</span><span class=\"s1\">&nbsp;Avoid heat treatments such as saunas, steam rooms, baths and showers for 48 hours.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s4\">â˜…</span><span class=\"s1\">&nbsp;Avoid exfoliation scrubs,&nbsp;AHA&rsquo;s,&nbsp;BHA&rsquo;s, and Vitamin A until the skin has normalised and does not feel sensitive. This can be up to 3-7 days.</span></p>\n<p class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s4\">â˜…</span><span class=\"s1\">&nbsp;Do not pick or pull at flaking skin as this will cause sensitivity and possible pigmentation.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s4\">â˜…</span><span class=\"s1\">&nbsp;Keep skin hydrated and apply the recommended post recovery cream as directed.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s4\">â˜…</span><span class=\"s1\">&nbsp;Avoid strenuous activities exercise, hot yoga and swimming for 48 hours.</span></p>\n<p class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s4\">â˜…</span><span class=\"s1\">&nbsp;Use a clean pillow case on the first evening.&nbsp;<br /> <br /> </span><span class=\"s4\">â˜…</span><span class=\"s1\">&nbsp;Avoid mobile phone touching skin for at least 2 hours.&nbsp;<br /> </span></p>\n<p class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s4\">â˜…</span><span class=\"s1\">&nbsp;Avoid heavy makeup for 48hours, mineral makeup in recommended, apply with a clean make up brush.</span></p>\n<p class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s4\">â˜…</span><span class=\"s1\">&nbsp;Avoid any other treatments for 2 weeks.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"p4\"><span class=\"s1\">In the event of any unexpected side affects such as persisting heat and itchiness in the area you must immediately&nbsp;contact the clinic within 24hours.</span></p>\n<p class=\"p5\"><span class=\"s5\"><br /> 01925 452745&nbsp;<br /> <a href=\"mailto:info@skingenius.co.uk\"><span class=\"s6\">info@skingenius.co.uk</span></a></span></p>\n</body>\n</html>', 0, 'email', '2019-08-21 17:24:50', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, '', '', 0, 'aftercare', '', '', 0, 1);
