                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           (225629, 0, 'price increase', 'price increase', '<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n</head>\n<body>\n<br /><br />\n<div>Hello!!,<br /><br />I hope you are well?<br /><br />Firstly i would like to thank you for your custom, as a small business owner loyal customers are priceless!!<br /><br />I just wanted to give you notice that i will be implementing&nbsp; a price increase on all dermal filler treatments. This the first price increase i have had in 12 years and is something i have thought long and hard about. The increase is a reflection of both the market and the investment over the years in my training, development and expertise. As I\'m&nbsp;sure you\'re aware Im extremely&nbsp;passionate about safety in aesthetics and i work very hard in ensure i am trained to a high level by some of the worlds most skill full injectors. Comparatively&nbsp;you will still be getting a great deal when compared to other advanced, medically trained, injectors.<br /><br />I have always used premium products and that is something that i will never compromise ensuring both safety and the best results!!<br /><br />The increase will take effect from the 1st of October.<br /><br />In other news......... look out for emails from me with some new packages incorporating both injectables and skincare. This will enable me to provide a more holistic approach to looking after you and your skin! There will be some fantastic free treatments&nbsp;within these packages and who doesn\'t&nbsp;love free stuff!! Even better, you will be able to split the cost monthly.<br /><br />I hope you have had a lovely summer and i look forward to seeing you very soon,<br /><br />Love,<br /><br />Luisa</div>\n</body>\n</html>', 0, 'email', '2019-09-09 09:15:20', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, '', '', 0, 'general', '', '', 0, 1);
