                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           (225692, 0, 'BHRT Follow Up Consultation Precare', 'Your BHRT/HRT Follow Up Consultation and Blood Test', '<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n</head>\n<body>\n<br /><img src=\"https://crm.pabau.com/cdn/template_archive/8188/template_attachments/d3729b029266e75922d8241ceed14892.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"473\" height=\"142\" /><br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Dear&nbsp;[APPOINTMENTNAME],<br /><br />Thank you for booking a&nbsp;BHRT/HRT&nbsp;Follow-Up Consultation with us. We hope your treatment has been going well.&nbsp;<br /><br />Before your appointment, we would like you to complete the following questionnaire to help us learn a little more about you.&nbsp;The General Health questionnaire will ask you questions regarding your personal, psychological, sexual and general health. It is essential that you submit&nbsp;this before your follow-appointment as&nbsp;it is required&nbsp;for your next appointment.<br /></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><br /><strong>General Health Questionnaire</strong><br />[MEDICALFORM&nbsp;id=277496]<br /></span></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">During your&nbsp;Follow-Up Consultation, your nurse will guide you through another questionnaire that will ask you questions surrounding menopausal symptoms. We will use this to see if the medication prescribed to you has been working or not. A blood test will also be repeated for another set of results and prescription.&nbsp;</span><br /><br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br /><br />About the&nbsp;BHRT&nbsp;Process<br /></strong></span></span></span>\n<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 2\">\n<div class=\"section\">\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\n<div class=\"column\">\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">A simple blood test can unlock exactly what your body needs to go through the menopause - naturally.&nbsp;Here at&nbsp;Silvery.Blue, we believe every woman deserves the time to explore her symptoms and every option available. We understand that, as women, we are not all the same . Our diagnosis relies on listening to your symptoms&nbsp;followed by a blood test that will pinpoint your exact hormone imbalance. Your results will be available one week later.&nbsp;We can then help you choose the most effective treatment plan that will benefit you and write you a prescription for this. Whether it is conventional&nbsp;HRT&nbsp;bio-identical&nbsp;HRT&nbsp;or a&nbsp;Mirena&nbsp;coil to give you progesterone &ndash; we can meet all of your needs in just one clinic.&nbsp;<br /><br /></span></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">If you feel the need to clarify or get more information, please feel free to get in touch with us.&nbsp;</span><br />\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Remember all information is kept strictly confidential and will not be shared with any third parties. We are always here to help.&nbsp;We hope you make most out of your consultation and we look forward to welcoming you to The Women&rsquo;s Health Clinic which is the medical arm of Silvery Blue<br /><br /></span></p>\n<table style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 16px; font-weight: normal; color: #666666; text-align: left; border-spacing: 0px;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"8\"><span style=\"color: 