                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           (226322, 0, 'Dermal Filler aftercare', 'Post treatment advice', '<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n</head>\n<body>\n<br /><br /><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><img src=\"https://crm.pabau.com/cdn/template_archive/8340/template_attachments/80b9b6940e4c81115202e1965c1bea25.PNG\" alt=\"\" /><br /><br /></span></div>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><br /><br />Hi [APPOINTMENTFIRSTNAME],<br /><br />Thank you for your visit to&nbsp;Nassif&nbsp;MedSpa&nbsp;on&nbsp;[ADATE]<br /><br />It takes approximately 3 weeks to see the full results of your dermal filler treatment.<br />Please allow enough time for the swelling to reduce, particularly with lips. It is perfectly normal for lips to feel a little lumpy for a period of 3 weeks after your procedure. This is simply fluid or bruising from the injection and will resolve quickly. Should you experience any persistent issues please get in touch.&nbsp;<br /><br /><br />Following your Dermal filler treatment, we have provided your aftercare advice that we would like you to follow-&nbsp;</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Do not wear makeup for at least 12 hours and keep the skin clean with normal cleansing. Do not use cleansing wipes as they may irritate the skin</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Avoid sun bathing, sun beds and extremes of heat for 14 days - failure to adhere to this has been shown to increase and prolong swelling</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Avoid vigorous exercise, extremes of heat or cold for 48 hours</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Avoid massage on the day of treatment. The doctor will advise you if otherwise</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Avoid alcohol for 24 hours after treatment</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Do not take ibuprofen based pain killers for 72 hours after treatment. Any pain can be treated with paracetamol</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">If your lips feel numb or desensitised, do not eat or drink within the first 4 hours as you may unknowingly burn or damage your mouth&nbsp;</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Do not manipulate injected areas</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Expect 10% of the final lip volume seen immediately after injecting to disappear (it is caused by swelling)</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Redness, swelling and bruising may be present in the injected areas</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Redness may last several hours after treatment</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Avoid aspirin and any other medications which may increase the risk of bruising further</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Apply cool compress and Arnicare cream if bruising further</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Make up may be applied to treated areas, although it is advisable to use sterile make-up and to wait 24h until applying</span></li>\n</ul>\n<br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">The following symptoms are perfectly normal (see below)-</span><br />\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Bruising - Most clients can resume normal daily activity immediately after treatment. On the rare occasion bruising does become visible, this does not affect the results of the filler. it takes time for the bruising to settle, we recommend that you apply cold packs immediately. Arnica tablets or cream may also help (check suitability with the pharmacist).</span></li>\n<li>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Swelling - Each client has different rates of healing. A swelling is normal and to be expected. It often peaks during the first 24hours post treatment and soon enough will&nbsp;subside. You will be able to enjoy the complete results after 3 weeks.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<br /><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Severe side effects:</span><br />\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Sever pain which is worsening</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Blanching (whitening skin) which is cool to the touch</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Blisters</span></li>\n</ul>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<br /><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Other symptoms:</span><br />\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Redness</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Warmth</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Spots</span></li>\n</ul>\n<br />\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><br /><strong>Please inform us immediately on our emergency contact / out of hours number - 07437049053 if you experience any of the severe side effects listed, or seek medical advice.</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><br />We look forward to seeing you again! If we can assist you further please contact us on&nbsp;<strong>0161 877 8444</strong>.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Warm wishes,</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Nassif&nbsp;MedSpa&nbsp;team&nbsp;</span></p>\n<br /><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a title=\"Nassif Med Spa\" href=\"https://twitter.com/nassifmedspauk\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://crm.pabau.com/cdn/template_archive/8340/template_attachments/642fbf0cbf4af8f9ff9776b363167856.png\" alt=\"\" /><br /><br /><br /></a><a title=\"Nassif Med Spa\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/NassifMedSpaUK/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://crm.pabau.com/cdn/template_archive/8340/template_attachments/563d0b09f2f1ab1a16d9ca1e2bae3cc8.PNG\" alt=\"\" /></a><a title=\"Nassif Med Spa\" href=\"https://www.instagram.com/nassifmedspauk/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://crm.pabau.com/cdn/template_archive/8340/template_attachments/c4161ab5ff5f0dd4ac4add27e187d392.PNG\" alt=\"\" width=\"63\" height=\"60\" /></a><a title=\"Nassif Med Spa\" href=\"https://twitter.com/nassifmedspauk\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://crm.pabau.com/cdn/template_archive/8340/template_attachments/c9ec4f991e617a918fbe0393a32bc9e0.PNG\" alt=\"\" width=\"58\" height=\"60\" /></a><a title=\"Nassif Med Spa\" href=\"https://twitter.com/nassifmedspauk\" target=\"_blank\"><br /></a></div>\n<br /><br /><br /><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</div>\n</body>\n</html>', 0, 'email', '2019-09-26 14:41:43', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, '', '', 0, 'aftercare', '', '', 0, 1),
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           (226454, 0, 'Student Confirmation', 'Your Booking Information', '<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n</head>\n<body>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://crm.pabau.com/cdn/template_archive/8325/template_attachments/0e6ab64d472438f4fe76dc6ab8831468.png\" alt=\"\" /><br /><img src=\"https://crm.pabau.com/cdn/template_archive//template_attachments/f466774a86edf71908f277600f690438.png\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</body>\n</html>', 0, 'email', '2019-09-28 09:20:39', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, '', '', 0, 'precare', '', '', 0, 1);
