e don\'t&nbsp;know this but as we age our bones reabsorb which is why we loose definition of the jaw, then add this to our mid face&nbsp;slipping south and it all equals jowls!!! This package will pack an amazing&nbsp;punch, why?? Well because for this complaint we get to use the formidable Volux, the newest member of the Vycross&nbsp;family. Both the chin and jaw will be treated to reduce sagging, signs of ageing and the sad look we women hate!! What\'s more......the results will last up to 18 months............yes i know, its brilliant!!<br /><br />Total cost &pound;1000 and will this you will receive 2 free chemical feels and post peel skincare worth over &pound;200 giving your skin an overhaul at the same time.....amazing!!<br /><br /><br />THE ONE FOR THE MOUTH.........<br /><br />I get so many of my patients complaining about the perioral&nbsp;area!!!! I hear comments such as.......\'i look sad, i feel old, my lips have disappeared\' yet its the treatment that worries you all the most!!! If treated correctly i can guarantee that no one will know and it will leave you looking fresh and much more youthful. This package will treat the lips, lines surrounding the lips, the corners of the mouth and nose to mouth lines......the ultimate anti-ageing combination!!<br /><br />Total cost &pound;860 and again you will receive 2 free chemical feels and post peel skincare.<br /><br /><br />&nbsp;If you have any questions about any of the packages please contact me and i hope you find something to suit you.<br /><br />I now offer Go Cardless&nbsp;direct debit scheme as a way of paying monthly for your treatments in advance and again if you would like more info on that just shout.<br /><br />Love,<br /><br />Luisa<br /><br /><br />\n</body>\n</html>', 0, 'email', '2019-10-18 10:33:20', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, '', '', 0, 'general', '', '', 0, 1),
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           (227915, 0, 'HydraFacial Pre and Post Care Instructions', 'Hydrafacial pre and post care', '<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n</head>\n<body>\n<div>Please find below all the care&nbsp;information you will need to follow prior and post to your treatment at Perfect Skin Solutions. Please read this carefully.&nbsp;<br /><strong><br />Hydrafacial&nbsp;Pre Aftercare Advice&nbsp;</strong></div>\n<div><br />\n<ul>\n<li>Avoid Retinol and&nbsp;high levels of AHA and BHA&nbsp;products&nbsp;for two days prior to your HydraFacial treatment</li>\n<li>Avoid the use of sunbeds or sun exposure for a minimum of one week before your treatment. If you are obviously sunburnt, you will not be able to be treated</li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Roaccutane patients must wait 12 months before being treated with HydraFacial</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Patients that have an allergy to shellfish, honey and aspirin cannot have this procedure</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">This treatment is not suitable for patients who are pregnant or lactating</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">You must wait for a minimum of two weeks AFTER your injectables (Dermal filler/ Anti-wrinkle injections and Profhilo) before having a HydraFacial procedure<br /></span></li>\n</ul>\n<div><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Hydrafacial skin treatments result in minimal to no downtime but create dramatic and visible results. Treatments may cause slight redness and tightness for a few hours. Most patients do not find it necessary to apply make up, as the skin will be smooth, dewy and radiant following treatment.&nbsp;<br /></span></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></div>\n<div><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Hydrafacial Aftercare Advice</strong></span></div>\n<div>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">For best results and to reduce the risk of complications, it is recommended that you use AlumierMD&nbsp;home care products post treatment<br /></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">After your treatment, your skin may feel warm to touch and look pink for a few hours. Any tingling sensation or pinkness will reside after a few hours</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Avoid Retinol for two days post-treatment. Salicylic and Pyruvic acid is fine to use.&nbsp;</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">You must wear a minimum of SPF 30 e.g AlumierMD Sheer Hydration</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Avoid waxing, threading and other methods of hair removal for one week</span></li>\n</ul>\n<div><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">If you do have any further questions, please do not hesitate to contact us on 02392 754 777 or via email&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:info@perfectskinsolutions.co.uk\">info@perfectskinsolutions.co.uk</a><br /><br />Kindest Regards,<br /><br />Perfect Skin Solutions<br /><br />121 Winter Road<br />Southsea<br />PO4 8DS<br /><br /><strong>Confidentiality Notice</strong><br />This communication and the information it contains:<br />(a) is intended for the person(s) or Organisation(s) named above and for no other persons or organisations and,<br />(b) may be confidential, legally privileged and protected by law.<br />Unauthorised use, copying or disclosure of any of it may be unlawful.<br />If you receive this communication in error, please notify us immediately, destroy any copies and delete it&nbsp;<br />from your computer system.</span></span>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br /><br /><br />\n</body>\n</html>', 0, 'email', '2019-10-18 17:21:24', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, '', '', 0, 'precare', '', '', 0, 1),
