                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           (227930, 0, 'Fat Freezing Information (NEW)', 'Fat Freezing Dr Tatiana Clinic', '<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n</head>\n<body>\n<h3><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://crm.pabau.com/cdn/template_archive/4627/template_attachments/16016910b65e372386428e425212b374.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"687\" height=\"200\" />Hello,</h3>\n<p class=\"p1\">Thank you for your enquiry about the Fat Freezing treatment.</p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; line-height: 100%;\" align=\"justify\"><span lang=\"en-GB\">Excess fat is a common problem. In many cases, small pockets of fat can be resistant to weight loss. No matter how much one diets or exercises, the stubborn areas of fat can remain e.g. under the chin, upper arms, around bra straps, abdomen, love-handles, thighs, and other areas.&nbsp;<br /><br /></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; line-height: 100%;\" align=\"justify\"><span lang=\"en-GB\"><strong>What is Fat Freezing &amp; how does it work?</strong><br /></span></p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Fat Freezing is designed to sculpt and treat the entire body.&nbsp;</span>The treatment is suitable for men and women of normal weight who have localised accumulations of fat which is resistant to diet and exercise.&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">By freezing the fat cells to -8C triggering apotosis, the fat cells are destroyed and the lymphatic system takes them away.&nbsp;<br /><br /></span></p>\n<p class=\"p2\"><strong><span class=\"s1\">What happens during the treatment?</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">During the treatment, your practitioner will apply a gel pad and applicator to the targeted area. The applicator delivers controlled cooling to the targeted fat. After 45-70 minutes, the practitioner will remove the&nbsp;applicator and massage the area to complete your treatment.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">It is common to experience some initial pulling and pinching during the process, but overall the procedure involves minimal pain.&nbsp;<br /><br />During the treatment you may want to read a book, work on your laptop or listen to music.</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; line-height: 100%;\" align=\"justify\"><span lang=\"en-GB\"><br /></span><strong>What areas can be treated with the Fat Freezing treatment?:&nbsp;<br /></strong></p>\n<ul class=\"ul1\">\n<li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s2\">upper and lower abdomen</span></li>\n<li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s2\">inner and outer thighs</span></li>\n<li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s2\">flanks (or love handles)</span></li>\n<li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s2\">arms</span></li>\n<li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s2\">chin area (or double chin)</span></li>\n<li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s2\">bra and back fat</span></li>\n<li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s2\">underneath the buttocks</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; line-height: 100%;\" align=\"justify\">Most frequent areas to treat with Fat&nbsp;Freezing are upper arms, abdomen and inner thighs.&nbsp;</p>\n<p lang=\"en-GB\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; line-height: 100%;\" align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n<div class=\"modal-header\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div id=\"before-after-carousel\" class=\"carousel slide\" data-ride=\"carousel\" data-interval=\"false\">\n<div class=\"carousel-inner\">\n<div class=\"carousel-item active\">\n<div class=\"container-fluid\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-8 offset-2 col-sm-6 offset-sm-0 col-md-5 offset-md-1\">\n<div class=\"card card-inverse before\"><br />\n<h3 class=\"card-title text-center\">Before&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; After</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p class=\"p1\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><strong><img src=\"https://crm.pabau.com/cdn/template_archive//template_attachments/cef1a14c100c4dd81c549fda86b39890.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"806\" height=\"316\" /><br />Results seen 4 weeks after treatment&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><strong>After the treatment:<br /></strong></p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Can go back to your normal lifestyle straight after the treatment.</span></p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Do listen to your body, </span></p>\n<ul class=\"ul1\">\n<li class=\"li2\"><span class=\"s1\">Wear comfortable clothing</span></li>\n<li class=\"li2\"><span class=\"s1\">Consider wearing&nbsp;compression clothing</span></li>\n<li class=\"li2\"><span class=\"s1\">Keep moving to reduce pain and inflammation</span></li>\n<li class=\"li2\"><span class=\"s1\">Report any severe side effects to us straight away</span></li>\n<li class=\"li2\"><span class=\"s1\">Maintain a healthy lifestyle </span></li>\n<li class=\"li1\"><span class=\"s1\">Consider having some radiofreqency treatments to improve the skin tighteness </span></li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p1\"><br /><strong>How many sessions are required?:<br /><br /></strong>You may need 1-3&nbsp;treatments on the same area to get the desired result every 6-8 weeks.&nbsp;<strong><br /></strong><br /><strong>When will I see results?:<br /></strong><br />It can take 3-6 month to see the full result, however some people do see results after a few weeks.<strong><br /></strong><br /><strong>How much does it cost?:</strong></p>\n<div>\n<table style=\"height: 196px;\" width=\"376\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border: none; padding: 0in;\" width=\"345\">\n<p><span style=\"background-color: #ff0000;\"><strong>Area<br /><br />1 Treatment</strong></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border: none; padding: 0in;\" width=\"73\">\n<p><span style=\"background-color: #ff0000;\"><strong>Price per treatment &pound;</strong></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border: none; padding: 0in;\" width=\"345\">\n<p><span style=\"background-color: #ff0000;\">2 Treatments&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border: none; padding: 0in;\" width=\"73\">\n<p><span style=\"background-color: #ff0000;\">&pound;&nbsp;</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border: none; padding: 0in;\" width=\"345\">\n<p><span style=\"background-color: #ff0000;\">&nbsp;3 Treatments</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border: none; padding: 0in;\" width=\"73\">\n<h3><span style=\"background-color: #ff0000;\">&nbsp;</span></h3>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border: none; padding: 0in;\" width=\"345\">\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.2in;\"><span style=\"background-color: #ff0000;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border: none; padding: 0in;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"73\">\n<p><span style=\"background-color: #ff0000;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n<em>*Please note that a deposit of <span style=\"background-color: #ff0000;\">&pound;500</span> is required in order to secure your treatment appointment with the balance&nbsp;paid on the day of treatment. We do not offer any payment plans.</em>&nbsp;<br /><em>** Please note that we request at least 48 hours notice for any cancellations or rescheduling appointments. If you are unable to provide at least 48 hours notice, your deposit will be forfeited.&nbsp;</em><br /><strong><br />Do you have any questions?&nbsp;</strong>We are here to make your treatment&nbsp;easy, comfortable and safe. If there&rsquo;s anything we can do to make sure you have an&nbsp;exceptional experience&nbsp;with us, please do let us know.<br /><br /><strong>Kind Regards,</strong>\n<p class=\"p1\"><strong>Dr Tatiana and Team</strong>&nbsp;<br />Dr Tatiana Aesthetic Dermatology Clinic<br />35&nbsp;Devonshire&nbsp;Place, London, W1G 6JP<br /><a href=\"http://www.drtatiana.co.uk\">www.drtatiana.co.uk</a>&nbsp;<br /><br />Bookings: +447718219145<br />Email:&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:info@drtatiana.co.uk\">info@drtatiana.co.</a>uk</p>\n</body>\n</html>', 0, 'email', '2019-10-21 12:53:49', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, '', '', 0, 'general', '', '', 0, 1),
