uld you have any further queries,&nbsp;please contact our friendly Front of House team who will be delighted to help.<strong><br /><br /></strong></span></span></div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<br /><!-- [if mso]><br /> </td><br /> <![endif]--> <!-- [if mso]><br /> </tr><br /> </table><br /> <![endif]--></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<br />\n<table class=\"mcnImageBlock\" style=\"min-width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; mso-table-lspace: 0pt; mso-table-rspace: 0pt; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\" border=\"0\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody class=\"mcnImageBlockOuter\">\n<tr>\n<td class=\"mcnImageBlockInner\" style=\"padding: 9px; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\" valign=\"top\"><img src=\"https://crm.pabau.com/cdn/template_archive/5617/template_attachments/663f2bbf607afe4efe40f7707dd9ac5c.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"594\" height=\"396\" /></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<br />\n<table class=\"mcnTextBlock\" style=\"min-width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; mso-table-lspace: 0pt; mso-table-rspace: 0pt; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\" border=\"0\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody class=\"mcnTextBlockOuter\">\n<tr>\n<td class=\"mcnTextBlockInner\" style=\"padding-top: 9px; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\" valign=\"top\"><!-- [if mso]><br /> <table align=\"left\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"100%\" style=\"width:100%;\"><br /> <tr><br /> <![endif]--> <!-- [if mso]><br /> <td valign=\"top\" width=\"599\" style=\"width:599px;\"><br /> <![endif]--><br />\n<table class=\"mcnTextContentContainer\" style=\"max-width: 100%; min-width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; mso-table-lspace: 0pt; mso-table-rspace: 0pt; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\" border=\"0\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" align=\"left\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"mcnTextContent\" style=\"mso-line-height-rule: exactly; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; word-break: break-word; color: #606060; font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 15px; line-height: 150%; text-align: left; padding: 0 18px 9px 18px;\" valign=\"top\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Exilis&nbsp;Elite Background Information&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>What is Exilis&nbsp;Elite?<br /></strong>Award-winning and clinically proven, Exilis&nbsp;Elite helps to contour the body, reduce stubborn pockets of fat and tighten and tone skin from head to toe.&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The system uses radio frequency to gently heat the dermis this stimulating new collagen growth deep within the dermal layer. Ultrasound technology&nbsp;targets unwanted fat cells, breaking them down so that the body can safely eliminate them.<br /><br />The procedure is pain-free and non-invasive and assures clients of proven&nbsp;results without the downtime, cost or possible side effects associated with surgery.&nbsp;<br /><br />Only available in the UK\'s leading medical aesthetic clinics, our highly trained and experienced aestheticians work closely with clients to achieve&nbsp;the desired outcome from treatment.&nbsp;</p>\n<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 1\">\n<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 1\">\n<div class=\"section\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\n<div class=\"column\">\n<p><strong>How does the treatment work?<br /></strong>Exilis&nbsp;Elite uses radio frequency to gently heat the dermis, thus stimulating new collagen growth deep within the dermal layer. The system also incorporates ultrasound technology to target unwanted fat cells, breaking them down so that the body can safely eliminate them. Exilis&nbsp;Elite offers the ideal face and body solution, enabling clients to reduce body fat and tighten skin without need for surgery.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Which areas can be treated?&nbsp;<br /></strong>The&nbsp;treatment system has two modules; one for fat reduction and one for skin tightening.<br /><br />The fat reduction module heats fat cells to a temperature that permanently destroys them and is highly effective on areas of stubborn, diet-and-exercise-resistant; fat on the stomach, inner and outer thighs, upper arms and back.&nbsp;<br /><br />The skin tightening module causes the collagen support tissues in the skin to remodel and tighten, thereby stimulating and strengthening the collagen network which improves skin laxity and texture, delivering excellent results on areas prone to sagging including the jowls, neck, decolletage, thighs and knees.&nbsp;<br /><br /><strong>How is the treatment carried out?<br /></strong>As every client\'s body, skin and required goals are unique, a detailed consultation with one of our expert aestheticians is essential prior to undergoing any advanced non-surgical treatment.&nbsp;<br /><br />During the consultation your aesthetician will discuss any problem areas, desired improvements, options available (including no treatment at all) and expected outcomes. A thorough medical history will be recorded and photographs taken to document your starting point prior to treatment.&nbsp;<br /><br /><strong>What results should I expect?<br /></strong>As every client and course of Exilis&nbsp;is unique, your aesthetician will discuss the specific expected outcomes of the programme prior to your initial treatment session.<br />&nbsp;<br />Widely speaking, following one or two facial treatments you may start to see a visible improvement to sagging skin and wrinkles, with the most dramatic results experienced after&nbsp;1 to 3 months after the course of treatment has been completed.&nbsp;<br /><br />Skin will appear firmer and smoother, with lines plumped and loose areas \'lifted\'. Areas of the body treated for fat reduction are likely to show visible improvement&nbsp;after just 4 treatment sessions; however more sessions may be required to achieve optimum body-contouring results.&nbsp;<br /><br /><strong>How does the treatment feel?<br /></strong>The Exilis&nbsp;Elite treatment is non-surgical, non-invasive and- on the whole- completely painless. At the beginning of the procedure, clients often experience a deep heating sensation whilst radio frequency&nbsp;energy is delivered to the deeper layers of the skin. The underside of the applicator provides cooling to the skin\'s surface, keeping you more comfortable during the treatment.&nbsp;<br /><br /><strong>Is there any down time?<br /></strong>Treatment with our Exilis&nbsp;Elite system is non-surgical, non-invasive and painless, with no down-time. Skin at the treatment site may be a little \'pink\' immediately after a treatment but this ordinarily subsides within 20 minutes post-procedure.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<br /><!-- [if mso]><br /> </td><br /> <![endif]--> <!-- [if mso]><br /> </tr><br /> </table><br /> <![endif]--></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<br />\n<table class=\"mcnButtonBlock\" style=\"min-width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; mso-table-lspace: 0pt; mso-table-rspace: 0pt; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\" border=\"0\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody class=\"mcnButtonBlockOuter\">\n<tr>\n<td class=\"mcnButtonBlockInner\" style=\"mso-line-height-rule: exactly; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; padding: 0 18px 18px 18px;\" align=\"center\" valign=\"top\"><br />\n<table class=\"mcnButtonContentContainer\" style=\"border-collapse: separate !important; border-radius: 3px; background-color: #e0c2c2; mso-table-lspace: 0pt; mso-table-rspace: 0pt; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"mcnButtonContent\"