in-width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; mso-table-lspace: 0pt; mso-table-rspace: 0pt; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\" border=\"0\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody class=\"mcnTextBlockOuter\">\n<tr>\n<td class=\"mcnTextBlockInner\" style=\"padding-top: 9px; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\" valign=\"top\"><br />\n<table class=\"mcnTextContentContainer\" style=\"max-width: 100%; min-width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; mso-table-lspace: 0pt; mso-table-rspace: 0pt; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\" border=\"0\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" align=\"left\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"mcnTextContent\" style=\"mso-line-height-rule: exactly; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; word-break: break-word; color: #606060; font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 15px; line-height: 150%; text-align: left; padding: 0 18px 9px 18px;\" valign=\"top\"><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: helvetica neue,helvetica,arial,verdana,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Thank you once again for visiting the clinic today for your appointment with&nbsp;[AWITH]. We really hope you enjoyed your experience here with us.</span></span></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: helvetica neue,helvetica,arial,verdana,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><br />Included below are our post treatment recommendations, which will help you achieve optimum results from your procedure. We hope you find these helpful, but as always, if you have any further queries or concerns, please don\'t hesitate to contact our friendly team who are always on hand and happy to help.&nbsp;</span></span></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: helvetica neue,helvetica,arial,verdana,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">In the meantime, we would be hugely grateful if you could spare a moment to share your experience and feedback with us. This feedback is invaluable to us in ensuring we are delivering the exceptional standards of client care that our customers except and deserve. To thank you for your time we will automatically enter you in to our monthly prize draw for the chance to win a &pound;50 face etc medispa&nbsp;gift card. To leave a review, simply click the button beneath the aftercare information, below.<br /><br />Thank you once again, we look forward to welcoming you to the clinic again soon</span></span></div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<br /><br /><!-- [if mso]><br /> </td><br /> <![endif]--> <!-- [if mso]><br /> </tr><br /> </table><br /> <![endif]--></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<br />\n<table class=\"mcnImageBlock\" style=\"min-width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; mso-table-lspace: 0pt; mso-table-rspace: 0pt; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\" border=\"0\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody class=\"mcnImageBlockOuter\">\n<tr>\n<td class=\"mcnImageBlockInner\" style=\"padding: 9px; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\" valign=\"top\"><img src=\"https://crm.pabau.com/cdn/template_archive/5617/template_attachments/663f2bbf607afe4efe40f7707dd9ac5c.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"594\" height=\"396\" /></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<table class=\"mcnTextBlock\" style=\"min-width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; mso-table-lspace: 0pt; mso-table-rspace: 0pt; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\" border=\"0\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody class=\"mcnTextBlockOuter\">\n<tr>\n<td class=\"mcnTextBlockInner\" style=\"padding-top: 9px; text-size-adjust: 100%; text-align: center;\" valign=\"top\"><br />\n<table class=\"mcnTextContentContainer\" style=\"max-width: 100%; min-width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; mso-table-lspace: 0pt; mso-table-rspace: 0pt; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\" border=\"0\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" align=\"left\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"mcnTextContent\" style=\"mso-line-height-rule: exactly; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; word-break: break-word; color: #606060; font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 15px; line-height: 150%; text-align: left; padding: 0 18px 9px 18px;\" valign=\"top\">\n<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 1\">\n<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 1\">\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\n<div class=\"column\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<p><strong>Liposuction Aftercare Information&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 1\">\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\n<div class=\"column\">\n<p>Every member of our clinic is committed to your satisfaction with the care you received today. It is important you feel that we have listened to, and responded to, all of your questions and concerns. Please do not hesitate to ask Mr Rhodes any questions you may have regarding your treatment today, and the steps you will need to take in the coming days to assure the results of your treatment meet your expectations. The following information will assist you in maximising your results, and minimising any potential complications from your treatment. Please consider these instructions in conjunction with any additional information provided to you by&nbsp;Mr Rhodes or another member of&nbsp;our team.</p>\n<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 1\">\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\n<div class=\"column\">\n<p>If you have any questions about any information provided to you today, please ask&nbsp;Mr Rhodes to clarify them for you. Specifically, you may be prescribed medication as part of your recovery, it is important to use any medication furnished to you exactly as directed by Mr Rhodes.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Wound Care<br /></strong>It is important to keep any incisions clean and dry while they heal. Therefore, soaking the area as in a bath, pool, etc, is not advised. It is acceptable to wash the skin around the incision with mild soap and warm water, assuring the entire area is subsequently thoroughly dried. If you have a dressing over the incision, please replace this if it becomes wet or soiled. Do not pick, pull, scratch, or otherwise stress the area of the incision. Do not use any creams or lotions on the incision without approval from your clinician.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p>After your procedure, you may need to wear a compression bandage for the next two to three weeks to reduce swelling. This should only be removed for showering. You will probably experience some pain, swelling and bruising immediately after the procedure, this is normal and your symptoms will start to improve over the next week or so. Generally the inflammatory reaction of the skin is brief, and is at its most significant 48 hours post procedure. You might also be given antibiotics to reduce the risk of infection.</p>\n<p>Following Liposuction &nbsp;it is important to treat the skin gently until completely recovered and the following advice should be followed-</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Avoid vigorous exercise for 7-14 days<br /><br /></li>\n<li>Avoid any heat treatments such as sun exposure, steam rooms or sauna for 7-14 days<br /><br /></li>\n<li>Avoid alcohol for 48 hours<br /><br /></li>\n<li>Keep the dressing on the incision site dry and in place for 5 days and then remove</li>\n<li>Before you take the dressing off, you must wash your hands with soap and water and then carefully remove. Do not touch the healing wound with your fingers. The healing wound can then be left without a dressing.<br /><br /></li>\n<li>Your usual pain killers may be taken to ease any discomfort you experience post procedure, however, aspirin must be avoided. In the unlikely event that you experience excessive swelling, bleeding or severe pain, you are advised to contact Orla Rhodes on 07879 404303 or attend A&amp;E.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<br /><!-- [if mso]><br /> </td><br /> <![endif]--> <!-- [if mso]><br /> </tr><br /> </table><br /> <![endif]--></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<br />\n<table class=\"mcnButtonBlock\" style=\"min-width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; mso-table-lspace: 0pt; mso-table-rspace: 0pt; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\" border=\"0\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody class=\"mcnButtonBlockOuter\">\n<tr>\n<td class=\"mcnButtonBlockInner\" style=\"mso-line-height-rule: exactly; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; padding: 0 18px 18px 18px;\" align=\"center\" valign=\"top\"><br />\n<table class=\"mcnButtonContentContainer\" style=\"border-collapse: separate !important; border-radius: 3px; background-color: #e0c2c2; mso-table-lspace: 0pt; mso-table-rspace: 0pt; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"mcnButtonContent\" style=\"font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; padding: 15px; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\" align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">Leave a <a href=\"https://uk.trustpilot.com/review/faceetcmedispa.co.uk\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">TrustPilot</span></a>&nbsp;review</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<br />\n<table class=\"mcnFollowBlock\" style=\"min-width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; mso-table-lspace: 0pt; mso-table-rspace: 0pt; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\" border=\"0\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody class=\"mcnFollo