are peeling. This can lead to scarring.</li>\n<li>Avoid applying make-up, including artificial tanning products, directly to the treatment area(s) for 24 hours.</li>\n<li>Avoid cleansing and scrubbing the skin and using any products containing active ingredients such as glycolic acid, salicylic acid, lactic acid, citric acid, retinol, hydroquinone etc for at least 48 hours post treatment.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; * your practitioner will provide you with products to use after your treatment with instructions of how to use them.</p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; * please note the above list of active ingredients is not an exhaustive and it is your responsibility to check if the product you wish to use is appropriate. Your practitioner will always be able to help&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;you if you have any enquiries.</p>\n<p><br /><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">WHAT TO WATCH OUT AFTER TREATMENT</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Any persisting pain or redness or swelling that is not settling might be an indication of skin infection. Please contact your doctor/practitioner in your local \'Eudai Clinic\' to discuss and receive advice.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Please ensure you keep the treatment area clean to avoid any skin infection risk. Some tips to do this are:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Use a fresh pillow-case after your treatment.</li>\n<li>Use fresh towels on the treatment area.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Please ensure you discuss your overall treatment programme with your doctor as this will enable you to receive the best results from treatment. [COMPANYNAME]&nbsp;also offers professional skin care advice and stocks many cosmeceutical products which will help you to enhance your outcome. </strong>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><br /> <br /> <br /> <br /> <br /> [COMPANYLOGO]</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\">\n<p>[COMPANYNAME]</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"20\">\n<p>p:</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p>[COMPANYPHONE]</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"20\">\n<p>a:</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p>[COMPANYSTREET]</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"20\">\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p>[COMPANYCITY],&nbsp;[COMPANYPOSTAL]<br /><br /></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"20\">\n<p>w:</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p>[COMPANYSITE] &nbsp;e: [COMPANYEMAIL]<a href=\"mailto:hello@thelovelyclinic.co.uk\"><br /> <br /> </a></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\">\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>For any medical emergencies related to your treatment with &lsquo;Eudai Clinic&rsquo;, please call:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>During office hours: 07495935197</li>\n<li>Out of office hours: 07495935197</li>\n</ul>\n</body>\n</html>', 0, 'email', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, '', '', 0, 'aftercare', '', '', 0, 1),
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           (232287, 0, 'Multiple failed login attempts blocked', 'Multiple failed login attempts', '<!DOCTYPE html><html><head></head><body><div><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://crm.pabau.com/cdn/template_archive/4555/template_attachments/f4eaf9904d857761e134a77f76dbf6c8.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"594\" height=\"198\" /></div><br /><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><br /><br /><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; color: #000080;\"><strong>We have temporarily locked your account due to security reasons<br /></strong></span><br /></span></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">We have identified multiple failed log in&nbsp;attempts&nbsp;from your email address.<br />Our threshold to lock your account is after 5 failed attempts.<br /><br />Pabau\'s system&nbsp;is built to prevent any illegal log ins or attempts with your credentials.<br />Every time someone attempts to log in with incorrect credentials,<br /> the lockout time will be extended by 15 minutes. During that time, no log in attempts can be made at all.<br /></span></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><br /><strong><span style=\"color: #000080;\">How do I get my account unlocked?</span></strong><br /><br /></span></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Unlocking your account happens automatically after the lockout timer expires, </span></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">where after entering the correct credentials, you will be logged in as usual.<br /><br /></span></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #000080;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">I can\'t tell how long is the lockout timer, how long do I have to wait?<br /><br /></span></strong></span></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">The lockout timer is intentionally hidden to not display the information</span></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> that potentially could be used by the attacker to his advantage to try again. <br /><br /><span style=\"color: #000080;\"><strong>Want to unlock your account immediately?</strong></span><br /><br />Contact our customer support&nbsp;team at&nbsp;<a class=\"c-link\" href=\"mailto:customersupport@pabau.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">support@pabau.com</a>&nbsp;and they will sort it out for you. </span></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">*You need to email our support team from the email that you want to&nbsp;unlock.<br /><br /></span></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #000080;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 204, 204); text-decoration: underline;\">Pabau CRM and Security</span></span><br /><br /></span></strong></span></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;Here at Pabau CRM&nbsp;we take security cases very seriously.<br />Our&nbsp;automatic tools are 24/7 enabled to secure your account in case of any illegal attempts to access it.<br /><br /></span></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">We strongly recommend to all companies to activate 2FA authentication for an extra-layer of security to logins. <br /><br />Kind regards,<br /><br /><em>- Your friends at Pabau<br /><br /><img src=\"https://crm.pabau.com/cdn/template_archive/4555/template_attachments/b0ca8a76210031a2e5917dc98ca6a954.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"708\" height=\"195\" /><br /><br /></em></span></div></body></html>', 29752, 'email', '2020-03-05 17:21:02', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, '', '', 0, 'general', '', '', 0, 1),
