                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           (233067, 0, 'It is a new day, let\'s bright in it up a bit', 'brighter day', '<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n</head>\n<body>\n<img src=\"https://crm.pabau.com/cdn/template_archive//template_attachments/0a4aed325f1a6165b45df6554f9a553c.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"https://crm.pabau.com/cdn/template_archive//template_attachments/3f50974b8ad15787418fb07c4ea7ffec.png\" alt=\"\" /><br /><br />\n<p>Dear Novello&nbsp;Skin subscribers,<br /><br />During the difficult times that we are all currently facing, we wanted to do our bit to help bring useful tips and positivity into as many people&rsquo;s lives as possible.<br /> &nbsp;<br /> In order to do this, we have decided to focus on providing you with valuable content to help brighten your day, even just a little bit!<br /> &nbsp;<br /> We will now be sharing content every few days with varying topics from keeping the kids entertained, to looking after your own wellbeing, trying some of the viral social media challenges that are currently circulating (we&rsquo;re sure you can imagine the entertainment that this will provide!)<br /> &nbsp;<br /> This content will be available via email and also on our social media platforms. Please feel free to share this content with your friends, family and colleagues to help as many people as possible see the light at the end of the tunnel.<br /> &nbsp;<br /> Right now, we can&rsquo;t control a lot of things but we, as individuals, can control:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>A positive attitude</li>\n<li>Kindness and grace</li>\n<li>How we choose to spend our time at home &ndash; make it fun!</li>\n</ul>\n&nbsp;<br /> Together we can rise to this challenge and we hope you enjoy our first piece of content coming over next few days.<br /><br />Stay safe and healthy!<br /><br />Best wishes<br />Novello&nbsp;Skin Team\n</body>\n</html>', 0, 'email', '2020-03-28 08:25:23', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, '', '', 0, 'marketing', '', '', 0, 67),
