<br />Payment can be made with Apple Pay or Credit / Debit card and receipts will be issued by email.&nbsp;<br />Please let us know in advance if you wish to collect your skincare products during your appointment we will have your products ready and waiting.</span></strong><br /><br /><br />Please notify us if any of the following applies to you prior to your appointments:<br /></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Have you or any of your household shown any&nbsp;of the following symptoms of&nbsp;COVID-19:</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><br />Fever<br /></span>&nbsp;\n<div class=\"_2cuy _3dgx _2vxa\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Persistent cough<br /><br /></span></div>\n<div class=\"_2cuy _3dgx _2vxa\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Shortness of breath<br /><br /></span></div>\n<div class=\"_2cuy _3dgx _2vxa\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Sore throat<br /><br /></span></div>\n<div class=\"_2cuy _3dgx _2vxa\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Persistent headache<br /></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Loss of taste or smell</span>&nbsp;</div>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<div class=\"_2cuy _3dgx _2vxa\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Has anyone you have been in contact with, been confirmed as positive for&nbsp;COVID-19?</span>&nbsp;</div>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<div class=\"_2cuy _3dgx _2vxa\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Has anyone you have been in contact with awaiting testing for&nbsp;COVID-19?</span>&nbsp;<br /><br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Have you, or anyone you know, been contacted by Test &amp; Protect?<br /><br /><br /></span></div>\n<div class=\"_2cuy _3dgx _2vxa\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Have you or anyone you have been in contact with travelled out with&nbsp;Scotland in the past 2 weeks?</span></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><br /><br />Due to our Social Distancing Policies we are operating a \'<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Hands off</span>\' service at&nbsp;Clinetix.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">At your allocated appointment time you will be provided entry to the clinic.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Our front of house team will open the clinic door for you.&nbsp;</span><br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">You will be asked to sanitise your hands on arrival.&nbsp;<br /><br />Our reception area has been arranged to allow social distancing, please allow 2 meter distance between yourself and others at all times.&nbsp;</span><br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">You will be welcomed by your practitioner&nbsp;and accompanied to the clinical treatment area.&nbsp;</span><br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Following completion of your consultation / treatment our team will guide you out of the clinical&nbsp;area to reception, doors will be opened on your behalf.&nbsp;<br /><br />Our front of house team will organise your return appointment.&nbsp;<br />Confirmation of this will be issued by email.<br /><br />We understand that this is a strange time for everyone.&nbsp;<br />Our priority is to ensure we can continue to offer the&nbsp;Clinetix&nbsp;high standard of care whilst adhering&nbsp;to our Social Distancing Policies to protect the health of our patients, team and families.<br /><br />Should you have any questions please do not hesitate to call us on 01467 629892.<br /></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;Please&nbsp;note parking outside the clinic is restricted.&nbsp;</span><br /><strong><a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/place/1+High+St,+Inverurie+AB51+3PN/@57.2825773,-2.375835,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m5!3m4!1s0x48844021dba5f9cb:0xdde9217d1361a5ca!8m2!3d57.2825773!4d-2.3736463\"><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #000000;\">Clinetix&nbsp;Grampian</span></a></strong><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">First Floor, 1 High St,&nbsp;Inverurie&nbsp;AB51 3QA</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">01467 629892</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Pay &amp; Display Parking available across from the clinic.</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&pound;0.50 per 30 minutes.&nbsp;<br /></span><br />\n<table style=\"height: 25px;\" width=\"809\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"background-color: #000000; text-align: center;\" colspan=\"2\" rowspan=\"3\">\n<p><span style=\"color: #ffffff; font-size: 16px;\">Appointment Terms and Conditions</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">We respectfully request 48 hours notice to cancel or reschedule your appointment.</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">To make any changes to your appointment please call the clinic directly on 01467 629892.</span><br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><em>A cancellation or non-show fee may be applied to future appointments for changes made with less that 48 hours notice.<br /></em><br />Due to&nbsp;Healthcare&nbsp;Improvement Scotland regulations we are unable to&nbsp;permit children access to clinical treatment areas. If you wish for a&nbsp;minor to&nbsp;accompany you to the appointment&nbsp;we respectfully request&nbsp;that you arrange&nbsp;supervision&nbsp;within the waiting area.&nbsp;<em>&nbsp;<br /></em></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Please click&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.clinetix.co.uk/terms-and-conditions/\" target=\"_blank\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?hl=en-GB&amp;q=https://mandrillapp.com/track/click/30787834/www.clinetix.co.uk?p%&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1527600095148000&amp;usg=AFQjCNGd3bWk3pmtEVcPCOetE3J3JGNt9w\">here</a>&nbsp;for full booking terms and conditions.</span>&nbsp;</span></p>\n<table style=\"height: 21px;\" width=\"810\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"background-color: #d10202; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #ffffff;\">The&nbsp;Clinetix&nbsp;team are available 24 hours a day.</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">If you have any questions following treatment please call 01467 629892&nbsp;<br />or<br />Out Of Hours&nbsp;Clinetix&nbsp;Emergency 07764348631 for urgent care following treatment.&nbsp;</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">www.Clinetix.co.uk&nbsp;</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</body>\n</html>', 0, 'email', '2020-06-25 10:52:26', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, '', '', 0, 'precare', '', '', 0, 1),
