"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Terms and Conditions</strong></span><br /><br /><br />Below you will see the terms and conditions that apply to your treatment or treatment programme.</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>The Elixir Clinic Terms and Conditions</strong></span><br /><br /><br />\n<div><strong>Cancellation and Refund Policy</strong></div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>The Elixir Clinic reserves the right to change the date or cancel your booking if its premises are closed due to the circumstances beyond its control, including but not limited to fire, disputes with employees, by order of any public authority or any other major event.</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>\n<div>Treatments that are missed or not rescheduled&nbsp;<span class=\"m_-8899516080361654244gmail-m_3624469252171998681gmail-aBn\"><span class=\"aBn\" tabindex=\"0\" data-term=\"goog_1843847625\"><span class=\"aQJ\">within 48 hours</span></span></span>&nbsp;of the appointment time will result in your deposit becoming non-refundable. Deposits are fully refundable if cancellation takes place more than 48 hours prior to the appointment time.&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #000000;\">All products including skin care and supplements are also non-refundable.</span></div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>All packages or treatments purchased in advance are non-refundable, however, we do accept amendments with 48 hours advance notice to The Elixir Clinic.</div>\n<br /><br /><br /><strong>Medical History Form<br /><br /></strong>All new clients will be requested to complete a Medical History Form before our practitioners can perform any treatments on you. When completing this form please advise us of any health conditions, allergies or injuries which could affect your service. It is your responsibility to let us know of any changes in your circumstances before your treatment goes ahead. We also reserve the right to ask you to complete the Medical History Form every 6 months ao that we can update our records.<br /><br /><br /><strong>Booking your Appointment<br /><br /></strong>All bookings requires a &pound;100 deposit at the time of making the reservation which is redeemable against any treatment.</div>\n</div>\n<span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://www.theelixirclinic.com/\" target=\"_blank\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?hl=en&amp;q=http://www.theelixirclinic.com/&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1499274112346000&amp;usg=AFQjCNF-suVarJ7KZ_uDpwBLaikQWMqkgg\"><br /></a></span></div>\n</div>\n<br /><br />\n</body>\n</html>', 0, 'email', '2020-07-21 16:49:57', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, '', '', 0, 'general', '', '', 0, 1);
