                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           (238849, 0, 'Pre appointment MEDICAL HISTORY', 'Your Pre-appointment Medical Questionnaire', '<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n</head>\n<body>\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Dear&nbsp;[APPOINTMENTFIRSTNAME],<br /><br /><strong>Important Medical History Questionnaire - Action Required</strong><br /><br />We\'re looking forward to seeing you at your appointment!<br /><br />During the current climate, as part of our Covid-19 policy,&nbsp;we would appreciate it if you could fill in this important medical history form prior to attending your appointment.<br />This is an important requirement, and allows us to reduce/eliminate paperwork that would otherwise be required when you attend. Even if you have filled out a medical history form before, we need to have an updated copy prior to each appointment; please be assured that everything we\'re doing is only in your best interest.<br /><br />If you need any assistance in completing the form, please don\'t hesitate to contact us.<br /><br />[MEDICALFORM id=303166]<br /><br />Kind wishes,<br /><br />Team at Aesthetique Clinic<br /><br /><strong>Aesthetique&nbsp;Clinic</strong><br /><strong>371 Fore Street, London, N9 0NR</strong><br /><strong>020 8803 7550</strong><br /><strong>reception@aesthetiqueclinics.com</strong></span>\n</body>\n</html>', 0, 'email', '2020-06-13 00:54:10', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, '', '', 0, 'confirmation', '', '', 0, 1),
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           (239350, 0, 'Pre care filler', 'Your Pre care advice :)', '<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n</head>\n<body>\n<br /><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Dear&nbsp;[LEADFNAME],</span><br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">We look forward to seeing you on the [ADATE].<img src=\"https://crm.pabau.com/cdn/template_archive/8439/template_attachments/dec6bc688425d4f1d278207028ed7a7a.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"17\" height=\"17\" /></span><br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">These are just simple steps you can follow in order to minimise the chances of bruising and swelling.</span><br /><br />\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Do not take any blood thinners such as : Aspirin, Ibuprofen or similar products (Advil, Motrin, Aleve) for 3-7 days prior to filler. (These agents can increase bruising and bleeding at the injection site due to its blood thinning properties)</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Avoid fish oil, Vitamin E, Gingko&nbsp;Biloba, St Johns Wart for 3-7 days prior to filler.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Eat Spinach, Kale and celery for 3- 7 days to boost your levels of Vitamin K.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Apply Arnica&nbsp;cream to areas most affected by bruising ( around the mouth and under eyes) for several days before your appointment.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Hydrate and eat a meal before the appointment.&nbsp;</span></li>\n</ul>\n<br />\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">We look forward to seeing you soon!</span><br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Very kind regards,</span><br /><br /><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Zuzu Aesthetics</span></strong></div>\n</body>\n</html>', 0, 'email', '2020-06-20 20:28:07', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, 0, '', '', 0, 'precare', '', '', 0, 1),
